Key.English: The prototype was destroyed before it reached your base...
Key.Spanish: El prototipo fue destruido antes de llegar a su base...
Key.Portuguese: O protótipo esteve destruído dantes de que consiga vossa base...
Key.Japanese: 試作兵器は基地につく前に破壊されました...
Key.Original: The prototype was destroyed before it reached your base...

Key.English: The pilots where killed before they reached the base...
Key.Spanish: Los pilotos murieron antes de llegar a la base...
Key.Portuguese: Os pilotos onde assassinados dantes de que conseguiram a base...
Key.Japanese: パイロットは基地に戻る前に死亡しました...
Key.Original: The pilots where killed before they reached the base...

Key.English: The enemies reached the cruise missile before us...
Key.Spanish: Los enemigos llegaron al misil de crucero antes que nosotros...
Key.Portuguese: Os inimigos conseguiram o míssil de cruzeiro dantes de que nos...
Key.Korean: 적이 크루즈 미사일에 아군보다 먼저 당도하였습니다.
Key.Japanese: 敵が我々よりも早く巡航ミサイルにたどり着きました...
Key.Original: The enemies reached the cruise missile before us...

Key.English: The enemy has launched the scud before we could destroy it...
Key.Spanish: El enemigo ha puesto en marcha el scud antes de poder destruirlo...
Key.Portuguese: O inimigo tem lançado o scud dantes de que o poderíamos destruir...
Key.Korean: 아군이 손도 쓰기전에 적이 스커드를 발사하였습니다..
Key.Japanese: 敵が我々よりも早くスカッドミサイルにたどり着きました...
Key.Original: The enemy has launched the scud before we could destroy it...

Key.English: The flag was not delivered to base...
Key.Spanish: La bandera no se entregó en la base...
Key.Japanese: 旗は基地に届きませんでした...
Key.Original: The flag was not delivered to base...

Key.English: Sidemission not resolved
Key.Spanish: Misión secundaria no resuelta
Key.Portuguese: Sidemission Não resolvido
Key.Japanese: サイドミッション未解決
Key.Original: Sidemission not resolved

Key.English: There is a radar tower on the top of mount Nebelspitze. Find it and destroy it.
Key.Spanish: Hay una torre de radar en la cima del monte Nebelspitze. ¡Búsquela y destrúyala!.
Key.Portuguese: Há uma torre de radar na parte superior de monte Nebelspitze. Encontra-o e destruí-lo
Key.Korean: Nebelspitze 산 정상에 레이더 타워가 있습니다. 찾아서 파괴하십시오.
Key.Japanese: Nebelspitze山の頂上にレーダータワーがある。探して破壊しろ。
Key.Original: There is a radar tower on the top of mount Nebelspitze. Find it and destroy it.

Key.English: Good job. The tower is down.
Key.Spanish: Buen trabajo. La torre está abajo
Key.Portuguese: Bom trabalho. A torre está caída
Key.Japanese: タワーの破壊を確認。よくやった。
Key.Original: Good job. The tower is down.

Key.English: A high enemy officer arrives today in a ruin called Rog. He is responsible for the death of many civilians. Eliminate him!
Key.Spanish: Un oficial de alto rango enemigo, se presenta hoy en las ruinas de Rog. Es el responsable de la muerte de muchos civiles. ¡Elimínelo!
Key.Portuguese: Um agente de inimigo alto chega hoje em uma ruína chamou Rog. É responsável para a morte de muitos civis. Elimina-lhe!
Key.Korean: 적군의 고위장교가 'Rog'라는 폐허에 오늘 도착하였다고 합니다. 그는 수많은 민간인을 사지로 몰아넣은 자입니다. 제거하십시오.
Key.Japanese: 敵の上級将校がRogと呼ばれる廃墟に到着する。彼は多くの民間人殺害に関わっている。排除しろ!
Key.Original: A high enemy officer arrives today in a ruin called Rog. He is responsible for the death of many civilians. Eliminate him!

Key.English: The enemy officer is dead. Good job.
Key.Spanish: El oficial enemigo está muerto. Buen trabajo.
Key.Portuguese: O agente de inimigo é morrido. Trabalho bom.
Key.Korean: 장교가 그 값을 물었습니다. 정의는 승리합니다. 수고하셨습니다.
Key.Japanese: 敵の将校の死亡を確認。よくやった
Key.Original: The enemy officer is dead. Good job.

Key.English: There is a artillery cannon on top of mount Vysota. Destroy it before enemy troops use it to attack Chernogorsk.
Key.Spanish: Hay un cañón de artillería en la cima del monte Vysota. Destruya el cañón de artillería antes de que las tropas enemigas lo use para atacar Chernogorsk.
Key.Portuguese: Há um canhão de artilharia acima de monte Vysota. Destrói-o dantes de que tropas de inimigo o utilizam para atacar Chernogorsk.
Key.Korean: Vysota산 정상에 적군의 포대가 발견되었습니다. 적이 체르노고르스크(Chernogorsk)를 공격할 때 사용할수 없게끔 파괴하십시오.
Key.Japanese: Vysota山の頂上に長距離砲がある。敵がこれを使ってChernogorskを攻撃する前に破壊しろ
Key.Original: There is a artillery cannon on top of mount Vysota. Destroy it before enemy troops use it to attack Chernogorsk.

Key.English: Good job. The artillery cannon is destroyed.
Key.Spanish: Buen trabajo. El cañón de artillería ha sido destruído.
Key.Portuguese: Trabalho bom. O canhão de artilharia está destruído.
Key.Japanese: 長距離砲は破壊された。よくやった。
Key.Original: Good job. The artillery cannon is destroyed.

Key.English: There is a lighthouse on Isle Skalisty. Enemy ships use it to find their way to the Chernarus south coast, destroy it.
Key.Spanish: Hay un faro en la Isla Skalisty. Los barcos enemigos lo utilizan para encontrar su camino a la costa sur de Chernarus, destrúyalo.
Key.Portuguese: Há um faro em Isle Skalisty. Barcos de inimigo utilizam-no para encontrar sua maneira ao Chernarus costa do sul, destruí-lo.
Key.Korean: Isle Skalisty에 위치한 등대를 적이 사용할수 없게끔 파괴하십시오.
Key.Japanese: Skalisty島に灯台がある。敵の船はそれを使ってChernarusの南岸に向かっている、それを破壊しろ。
Key.Original: There is a lighthouse on Isle Skalisty. Enemy ships use it to find their way to the Chernarus south coast, destroy it.

Key.English: Good job. The lighthouse is destroyed.
Key.Spanish: Buen trabajo. El faro ha sido destruído.
Key.Portuguese: Trabalho bom. O faro está destruído.
Key.Japanese: よくやった。灯台は破壊された
Key.Original: Good job. The lighthouse is destroyed.

Key.English: A high enemy officer makes holidays in Kamyshovo. Eliminate him !
Key.Spanish: Un oficial de alto rango enemigo está de vacaciones en Kamyshovo. ¡Elimínelo!
Key.Portuguese: Umas marcas de agente de inimigo altas férias em Kamyshovo. Elimina-lhe !
Key.Korean: 적 고위장교가 Kamyshovo에서 휴가를 즐기고있다고합니다. 그에게 편안한 휴가를 선물해주십시오.
Key.Japanese: 敵高級将校がKamyshovoで休暇を過ごしている。彼を排除しろ!
Key.Original: A high enemy officer makes holidays in Kamyshovo. Eliminate him !

Key.English: Good job. The enemy officer is dead.
Key.Spanish: Buen trabajo. El oficial enemigo está muerto.
Key.Portuguese: Trabalho bom. O agente de inimigo é morrido.
Key.Japanese: 敵の将校の死亡を確認。よくやった。
Key.Original: Good job. The enemy officer is dead.

Key.English: The enemy prime minister visits some troops near Lopatino. Eliminate him !
Key.Spanish: El Primer Ministro enemigo está visitando a sus tropas cerca de Lopatino. ¡Elimínelo!
Key.Portuguese: As visitas de premiê do inimigo algumas tropas próximos Lopatino. Elimina-lhe !
Key.Korean: 적의 총리가 Lopatino 주변에 있는 부대를 방문하였습니다. 후회하게 해주십시오.
Key.Japanese: 敵の首相がLopatino近くの部隊を訪問する。彼を排除しろ!
Key.Original: The enemy prime minister visits some troops near Lopatino. Eliminate him !

Key.English: Good job. The prime minister is dead.
Key.Spanish: Buen trabajo. El primer ministro ha muerto.
Key.Portuguese: Trabalho bom. O premiê é morrido.
Key.Japanese: 首相の死亡を確認。よくやった。
Key.Original: Good job. The prime minister is dead.

Key.English: The enemy uses a radio tower to command its armored troops. Simple task, destroy it.
Key.Spanish: The enemy uses a radio tower to command its armored troops. Simple task, destroy it.
Key.Portuguese: The enemy uses a radio tower to command its armored troops. Simple task, destroy it.
Key.Korean: Lysina 산 정상에 라디오 타워가 있습니다. 적은 해당 기지를 통해 기갑병력을 통솔하고있다 합니다. 무력화하고 파괴시키십시오.
Key.Japanese: Lysina山の頂上にラジオタワーがある。敵はこれを装甲車両隊の指揮に利用してるようだ。それを破壊しろ。
Key.Original: The enemy uses a radio tower to command its armored troops. Simple task, destroy it.

Key.English: There is a transformer station in Petrovka. The enemy uses it for some experiments in a laboratory in Krasnostav. Simple task, destroy it.
Key.Spanish: Hay una estación de transformadores en Petrovka. El enemigo la utiliza para algunos experimentos en un laboratorio en Krasnostav. Tarea fácil, destrúyala.
Key.Portuguese: Há uma estação de transformador em Petrovka. Os usos de inimigo ele para alguns experimentos em um laboratório em Krasnostav. Tarefa singela, destruí-lo.
Key.Korean: Petrovka에 위치한 transformer를 krasnostav 연구소에서 사용중. 파괴
Key.Japanese: Petrovkaに変電所がある。敵はKrasnostavの研究所での実験に利用しているようだ。簡単な任務だ、それを破壊しろ。
Key.Original: There is a transformer station in Petrovka. The enemy uses it for some experiments in a laboratory in Krasnostav. Simple task, destroy it.

Key.English: Good job. The transformer station is down.
Key.Spanish: Buen trabajo. La estación transformadora ha sido destruída.
Key.Portuguese: Trabalho bom. A estação de transformador é abaixo.
Key.Japanese: よくやった。変電所は破壊された。
Key.Original: Good job. The transformer station is down.

Key.English: There is a radio tower on the top of mount Malinovka. The enemy uses it to command its marine task forces. Simple task, destroy it.
Key.Spanish: Hay una torre de radio en la cima del monte Malinovka. El enemigo la usa para controlar a sus tropas de comandos marinos. El único objetivo, destruir la torre.
Key.Portuguese: There is a radio tower on the top of mount Malinovka. The enemy uses it to command its marine task forces. Simple task, destroy it
Key.Japanese: Malinovka山の頂上にラジオタワーがある。敵はこれを海上タスクフォースの指揮に利用してるようだ。それを破壊しろ。
Key.Original: There is a radio tower on the top of mount Malinovka. The enemy uses it to command its marine task forces. Simple task, destroy it.

Key.English: A high enemy officer arrives today in Olsha. He is responsible for the production of biological and chemical weapons. Eliminate him !
Key.Spanish: Un alto oficial enemigo llega hoy a Olsha. Es el responsable de la producción de armas biológicas y químicas. ¡Elimínelo!
Key.Portuguese: Um agente de inimigo alto chega hoje em Olsha. É responsável para a produção de biológico e armas químicas. Elimina-lhe
Key.Japanese: 敵高級将校がOlshaに到着した。彼は生物化学兵器の製造にかかわってる。彼を排除しろ!
Key.Original: A high enemy officer arrives today in Olsha. He is responsible for the production of biological and chemical weapons. Eliminate him !

Key.English: A high enemy government member visits Berezino today. He wants to take a look at the local ship production in the Berezino shipyard. Eliminate him !
Key.Spanish: Un miembro del gobierno enemigo se encuentra hoy de visita en Berezino. Quiere echar un vistazo a la producción de armas. ¡Elimínelo!
Key.Portuguese: Um membro de governo de inimigo alto visitas Berezino hoje. Quer tomar uma mirada na produção de barco local no Berezino shipyard. Elimina-lhe !
Key.Japanese: 敵の政府の高官が今日Berezinoを訪れる。彼はBerezino造船所で地元の船の生産を視察するようだ。彼を排除しろ!
Key.Original: A high enemy government member visits Berezino today. He wants to take a look at the local ship production in the Berezino shipyard. Eliminate him !

Key.English: The government member is dead. Good job.
Key.Spanish: El miembro gubernamental está muerto. Buen trabajo.
Key.Portuguese: O membro de governo é morrido. Trabalho bom.
Key.Japanese: 政府高官の死亡を確認。よくやった。
Key.Original: The government member is dead. Good job.

Key.English: An enemy train is waiting in Elektrozavodsk for loading tanks and fuel. Find the train and destroy it!
Key.Spanish: Un tren enemigo está a la espera en Elektrozavodsk para la carga de tanques y combustible. ¡Encuentre el tren y destrúyalo!
Key.Portuguese: Um trem de inimigo está esperando em Elektrozavodsk para carregar tanques e combustível. Encontrar o trem e destruí-lo!
Key.Japanese: 敵の列車がElektrozavodskで戦車と燃料の積み込みを待っている。この列車を見つけ出して破壊しろ!
Key.Original: An enemy train is waiting in Elektrozavodsk for loading tanks and fuel. Find the train and destroy it!

Key.English: Good job. The train is down...
Key.Spanish: Buen trabajo. El tren ha sido destruído...
Key.Portuguese: Trabalho bom. Ou trem é fazer
Key.Korean: Good job. The train is down...
Key.Japanese: よくやった。列車は破壊された。
Key.Original: Good job. The train is down...

Key.English: Good job. You got the prototype plane.
Key.Spanish: Buen trabajo. Tiene el avión prototipo.
Key.Portuguese: Trabalho bom. Conseguia o avião de protótipo .
Key.Korean: Good job. You got the prototype plane.
Key.Japanese: よくやった。試作飛行機を手に入れた。
Key.Original: Good job. You got the prototype plane.

Key.English: The enemy is testing a new protoype plane at Balota airfield. Steal it and bring it to the flag at your base.
Key.Spanish: El enemigo está probando un nuevo prototipo de avión en el aeródromo de Balota. Coja el prototipo de avión y llévelo a la bandera de su base.
Key.Portuguese: O inimigo está provando um novo protoype avião em Balota aeródromo. Rouba-o e trazer à bandeira em vossa base.
Key.Korean: The enemy is testing a new protoype plane at Balota airfield. Steal it and bring it to the flag at your base.
Key.Japanese: Balota飛行場で敵が新型試作飛行機のテスト中だ。これを盗み出して基地に持ち帰れ。
Key.Original: The enemy is testing a new protoype plane at Balota airfield. Steal it and bring it to the flag at your base.

Key.English: The enemy is testing a new protoype plane at an airfield. Steal it and bring it to the flag at your base.
Key.Spanish: The enemy is testing a new protoype plane at an airfield. Steal it and bring it to the flag at your base.
Key.Portuguese: The enemy is testing a new protoype plane at an airfield. Steal it and bring it to the flag at your base.
Key.Korean: The enemy is testing a new protoype plane at an airfield. Steal it and bring it to the flag at your base.
Key.Japanese: 敵が新型試作飛行機のテスト中だ。これを盗み出して基地に持ち帰れ。
Key.Original: The enemy is testing a new protoype plane at an airfield. Steal it and bring it to the flag at your base.

Key.English: An enemy convoy is on route from Orlovets to Sosnovka. Find it and destroy it.
Key.Spanish: Un convoy está en ruta de Orlovets a Sosnovka. Búsquelo y destrúyalo.
Key.Portuguese: Um convoy de inimigo é em cima rota de Orlovets a Sosnovka. Encontra-o e destruí-lo.
Key.Korean: An enemy convoy is on route from Orlovets to Sosnovka. Find it and destroy it.
Key.Japanese: 敵の護送隊がOrlovetsからSosnovkaへ向かっている。それを見つけて破壊しろ。
Key.Original: An enemy convoy is on route from Orlovets to Sosnovka. Find it and destroy it.

Key.English: Good job. The convoy is down.
Key.Spanish: Buen trabajo. El convoy ha sido destruído.
Key.Portuguese: Trabalho bom. O convoy é abaixo.
Key.Korean: Good job. The convoy is down.
Key.Japanese: よくやった。護送隊は破壊された。
Key.Original: Good job. The convoy is down.

Key.English: An enemy convoy is on route from Gvozdno to Pusta. Find it and destroy it.
Key.Spanish: Un convoy está en ruta de Gvozdno a Pusta. Búsquelo y destrúyalo.
Key.Portuguese: Um convoy de inimigo é em cima rota de Gvozdno a Pusta. Encontra-o e destruí-lo
Key.Korean: An enemy convoy is on route from Gvozdno to Pusta. Find it and destroy it.
Key.Japanese: 敵の護送隊がGvozdnoからPustaへ向かっている。それを見つけて破壊しろ。
Key.Original: An enemy convoy is on route from Gvozdno to Pusta. Find it and destroy it.

Key.English: An enemy convoy is on route from Kozlovka to Msta. Find it and destroy it.
Key.Spanish: Un convoy está en ruta de Kozlovka a Msta. Búsquelo y destrúyalo.
Key.Portuguese: Um convoy de inimigo é em cima rota de Kozlovka a Msta. Encontra-o e destruí-lo.
Key.Korean: An enemy convoy is on route from Kozlovka to Msta. Find it and destroy it.
Key.Japanese: 敵の護送隊がKozlovkaからMstaへ向かっている。それを見つけて破壊しろ。
Key.Original: An enemy convoy is on route from Kozlovka to Msta. Find it and destroy it.

Key.English: A high enemy officer visits the enemy troops today in Teufelsschloss. He is a personal friend of the enemy leader. Eliminate him!
Key.Spanish: Un oficial de alto rango enemigo se encuentra visitando a sus tropas cerca de Teufelsschloss. Es amigo personal del líder enemigo. ¡Elimínelo!
Key.Portuguese: Um agente de inimigo alto visita as tropas de inimigo hoje em Teufelsschloss. É um amigo pessoal do dirigente de inimigo. Elimina-lhe!roy o.
Key.Korean: A high enemy officer visits the enemy troops today in Teufelsschloss. He is a personal friend of the enemy leader. Eliminate him!
Key.Japanese: 敵高級将校が今日Teufelsschlossの敵軍を訪ねる。彼は敵リーダーの個人的な友人のようだ。彼を排除しろ!
Key.Original: A high enemy officer visits the enemy troops today in Teufelsschloss. He is a personal friend of the enemy leader. Eliminate him!

Key.English: The enemy uses a fuelstation located near Bor to refuel its vehicles. Simple task, destroy it to cut down fuel supplies.
Key.Spanish: El enemigo utiliza una estación de combustible cerca de Bor para repostar sus vehículos. La tarea es simple, destrúyala para reducir los suministros.
Key.Portuguese: O inimigo utiliza um fuelstation localizou próximo Bor a refuel seus veículos. Tarefa singela, destruí-lo para cortar abaixo fornecimentos de combustível.
Key.Korean: The enemy uses a fuelstation located near Bor to refuel its vehicles. Simple task, destroy it to cut down fuel supplies.
Key.Japanese: 敵はBor近くの給油所を使って車両に燃料を補給している。 簡単なミッションだ、燃料供給を絶つためにそれを破壊しろ。
Key.Original: The enemy uses a fuelstation located near Bor to refuel its vehicles. Simple task, destroy it to cut down fuel supplies.

Key.English: Good job. The fuelstation is down.
Key.Spanish: Buen trabajo. La estación de combustible ha sido destruída.
Key.Portuguese: Trabalho bom. O fuelstation é abaixo.
Key.Korean: Good job. The fuelstation is down.
Key.Japanese: よくやった。給油所は破壊された。
Key.Original: Good job. The fuelstation is down.

Key.English: Intel has got some information about a specops camp near Vybor. Find it and eliminate all specops there before they try to sabotage something....
Key.Spanish: El servicio de intelgencia informa de un campamento enemigo de saboteadores cerca de Vybor. Búsquelo y elimine a todos ellos, antes de que traten de sabotear....
Key.Portuguese: Intel Tem alguma informação sobre um specops o acampamento próximo Vybor. Encontra-o e eliminar todo specops ali dantes de que provam a sabotagem algo....
Key.Korean: Intel has got some information about a specops camp near Vybor. Find it and eliminate all specops there before they try to sabotage something....
Key.Japanese: 情報部はVybor近くの特殊部隊キャンプに関する情報を手に入れた。キャンプを見つけて特殊部隊が何らかの破壊活動をする前に殺害しろ。
Key.Original: Intel has got some information about a specops camp near Vybor. Find it and eliminate all specops there before they try to sabotage something....

Key.English: Good job. The specops are eliminated.
Key.Spanish: Buen trabajo. Los specops han sido eliminados.
Key.Portuguese: Trabalho bom. O specops está eliminado.
Key.Korean: Good job. The specops are eliminated.
Key.Japanese: よくやった。特殊部隊は排除された。
Key.Original: Good job. The specops are eliminated.

Key.English: Intel has got some information about a specops camp in the north. Find it and eliminate all specops there before they try to sabotage something....
Key.Spanish: El servicio de intelgencia informa de un campamento enemigo de saboteadores en el norte. Búsquelo y elimine a todos ellos, antes de que traten de sabotear....
Key.Portuguese: Intel Tem alguma informação sobre um specops acampamento no do norte. Encontra-o e eliminar todo specops ali dantes de que provam a sabotagem algo...
Key.Korean: Intel has got some information about a specops camp in the north. Find it and eliminate all specops there before they try to sabotage something....
Key.Japanese: 情報部は北部にある特殊部隊キャンプに関する情報を手に入れた。キャンプを見つけて特殊部隊が何らかの破壊活動をする前に殺害しろ。
Key.Original: Intel has got some information about a specops camp in the north. Find it and eliminate all specops there before they try to sabotage something....

Key.English: There is a radio tower on top of mount Baranchik. This is one of the many radio towers that the enemy uses to communicate with its troops. Simple task, destroy it.
Key.Spanish: Hay una torre de radio en lo alto del monte de Baranchik. Busque la torre de radio que forma parte de una gran red de comunicación entre las tropas enemigas. ¡Detrúyala!.
Key.Portuguese: Há uma torre radiofónica acima de monte Baranchik. Isto é um das muitas torres radiofónicas que os usos de inimigo para comunicar com suas tropas. Tarefa singela, destruí-lo
Key.Korean: There is a radio tower on top of mount Baranchik. This is one of the many radio towers that the enemy uses to communicate with its troops. Simple task, destroy it.
Key.Japanese: Baranchik山の頂上にラジオタワーがある。これは多くある敵軍通信用のタワーの一つだ。探して破壊しろ。
Key.Original: There is a radio tower on top of mount Baranchik. This is one of the many radio towers that the enemy uses to communicate with its troops. Simple task, destroy it.

Key.English: The enemy has a bunker south of Vyshnoye. Enemy government uses this bunker for emergeny situations. Destroy the radar tower there to cut down the ability for them to communicate.
Key.Spanish: El enemigo tiene un búnker al sur de Vyshnoye. El gobierno enemigo usa el búnker para situaciones de emergencia. Destruya la torre del radio para reducir las comunicaciones enemigas.
Key.Portuguese: O inimigo tem um sul de bunker de Vyshnoye. Governo de inimigo utiliza este bunker para emergeny situações. Destruir a torre de radar ali para cortar abaixo a capacidade para eles para comunicar.
Key.Korean: The enemy has a bunker south of Vyshnoye. Enemy government uses this bunker for emergeny situations. Destroy the radar tower there to cut down the ability for them to communicate.
Key.Japanese: Vyshnoyeの北に敵のバンカーがある。 敵の政府は緊急事態にこのバンカーを使用する。 そこにあるレーダータワーを破壊して、敵の通信能力を絶て。
Key.Original: The enemy has a bunker south of Vyshnoye. Enemy government uses this bunker for emergeny situations. Destroy the radar tower there to cut down the ability for them to communicate.

Key.English: There is an enemy tank depot in a village near Dubrovka. Destroy all tanks there to weaken the enemy troops.
Key.Spanish: Buscar un depósito de tanques enemigos en un pueblo cerca de Dubrovka. Destruya todos los tanques para debilitar las tropas enemigas.
Key.Portuguese: There is an enemy tank depot in a village near Dubrovka. Destroy all tanks there to weaken the enemy troops.
Key.Korean: There is an enemy tank depot in a village near Dubrovka. Destroy all tanks there to weaken the enemy troops.
Key.Japanese: Dubrovka近くの村に戦車集積所がある。 そこにあるすべての戦車を破壊して敵軍を弱体化しろ。
Key.Original: There is an enemy tank depot in a village near Dubrovka. Destroy all tanks there to weaken the enemy troops.

Key.English: Good job. All tanks are down.
Key.Spanish: Buen trabajo. Todos los depósitos has sido destruídos.
Key.Portuguese: Trabalho bom. Todos os tanques são abaixo.
Key.Korean: Good job. All tanks are down.
Key.Japanese: よくやった。戦車はすべて破壊された。
Key.Original: Good job. All tanks are down.

Key.English: Enemy forces are testing an enhanced tank version at Pobeda-Damm. Your mission is to steal it and bring it to the flag at your base.
Key.Spanish: Las fuerzas enemigas tiene un prototipo de tanque en pruebas en Pobeda-Damm. Su misión es cojer el prototipo de tanque y llevarlo a la bandera de su base.
Key.Portuguese: Forças de inimigo estão provando uma versão de tanque realçada em Pobeda-Damm. Vossa missão é para roubá-lo e trazer à bandeira em vossa base
Key.Korean: Enemy forces are testing an enhanced tank version at Pobeda-Damm. Your mission is to steal it and bring it to the flag at your base.
Key.Japanese: 敵は改良型の戦車をPobeda-Dammでテスト中だ。君の任務はこれを盗み出して基地に持ち帰ることだ。
Key.Original: Enemy forces are testing an enhanced tank version at Pobeda-Damm. Your mission is to steal it and bring it to the flag at your base.

Key.English: Good job. You got the enhanced tank version.
Key.Spanish: Buen trabajo. Tiene la versión mejorada del tanque.
Key.Portuguese: Trabalho bom. Conseguia a versão de tanque realçada .
Key.Korean: Good job. You got the enhanced tank version.
Key.Japanese: よくやった。改良型の戦車を手に入れた。
Key.Original: Good job. You got the enhanced tank version.

Key.English: There is an enemy tank depot in Mogilevka. Destroy all tanks there to weaken the enemy troops.
Key.Spanish: Buscar un depósito de tanques enemigos en Mogilevka. Destruya todos los tanques para debilitar al enemigo.
Key.Portuguese: Há um depósito de tanque do inimigo em Mogilevka. Destruir todos os tanques ali para debilitar as tropas de inimigo.
Key.Korean: There is an enemy tank depot in Mogilevka. Destroy all tanks there to weaken the enemy troops.
Key.Japanese: Mogilevkaに戦車集積所がある。 そこにあるすべての戦車を破壊して敵軍を弱体化しろ。
Key.Original: There is an enemy tank depot in Mogilevka. Destroy all tanks there to weaken the enemy troops.

Key.English: This time we want to provoke the enemy. Find the enemy flag in Shakhovka and bring it back to the flag at your base.
Key.Spanish: Esta vez queremos provocar al enemigo. Busque la bandera enemiga en Shakhovka y llévela a su base.
Key.Portuguese: Este tempo queremos provocar o inimigo. Encontrar a bandeira de inimigo em Shakhovka e trazê-lo atrás à bandeira em vossa base.
Key.Korean: This time we want to provoke the enemy. Find the enemy flag in Shakhovka and bring it back to the flag at your base.
Key.Japanese: 今回私たちは敵を誘い出したい。 Shakhovkaで敵の旗を見つけ、基地に持ち帰れ。
Key.Original: This time we want to provoke the enemy. Find the enemy flag in Shakhovka and bring it back to the flag at your base.

Key.English: Good job. The enemy flag is in our base.
Key.Spanish: Buen trabajo. La bandera enemiga está en nuestra base.
Key.Portuguese: Trabalho bom. A bandeira de inimigo é em nossa base.
Key.Korean: Good job. The enemy flag is in our base.
Key.Japanese: よくやった。旗は無事に基地に届いた
Key.Original: Good job. The enemy flag is in our base.

Key.English: We want to provoke the enemy. Find the enemy flag in Bor and bring it back to the flag at your base.
Key.Spanish: Queremos provocar al enemigo. Busque la bandera enemiga en Bor y llévela a su base.
Key.Portuguese: Queremos provocar o inimigo. Encontrar a bandeira de inimigo em Bor e trazê-lo atrás à bandeira em vossa base
Key.Korean: We want to provoke the enemy. Find the enemy flag in Bor and bring it back to the flag at your base.
Key.Japanese: 今回私たちは敵を誘い出したい。 Borで敵の旗を見つけ、基地に持ち帰れ。
Key.Original: We want to provoke the enemy. Find the enemy flag in Bor and bring it back to the flag at your base.

Key.English: There is a transformer station in Ioannina. The enemy uses it for its communication relais stations. Simple task, destroy it.
Key.Spanish: Hay una estación de transformadores en Ioannina. El enemigo lo usa para sus estaciones repetidoras de comunicación. tarea sencilla, destrúyala.
Key.Portuguese: Há uma estação de transformador em Ioannina. Os usos de inimigo ele para sua comunicação relais estações. Tarefa singela, destruí-lo.
Key.Korean: There is a transformer station in Ioannina. The enemy uses it for its communication relais stations. Simple task, destroy it.
Key.Japanese: Ioanninaに変電所がある。 敵は通信リレーステーションにそれを使用している。 簡単な任務だ、それを破壊しろ。
Key.Original: There is a transformer station in Ioannina. The enemy uses it for its communication relais stations. Simple task, destroy it.

Key.English: There is a transformer station in Novy Sobor. The enemy uses it for its communication relais stations. Simple task, destroy it.
Key.Spanish: Hay una estación de transformadores en Novy Sobor. El enemigo la utiliza en sus estaciones de relés de comunicaciones. Tarea sencilla, destrúyala.
Key.Portuguese: Há uma estação de transformador em Novy Sobor. Os usos de inimigo ele para sua comunicação relais estações. Tarefa singela, destruí-lo.
Key.Korean: There is a transformer station in Novy Sobor. The enemy uses it for its communication relais stations. Simple task, destroy it.
Key.Japanese: Novy Soborに変電所がある。 敵は通信リレーステーションにそれを使用している。 簡単な任務だ、それを破壊しろ。
Key.Original: There is a transformer station in Novy Sobor. The enemy uses it for its communication relais stations. Simple task, destroy it.

Key.English: Find the enemy flag in Tulga and bring it back to the flag at your base.
Key.Spanish: Busque la bandera enemiga en Tulga y llévela a la bandera de su base.
Key.Portuguese: Encontrar a bandeira de inimigo em Tulga e trazê-lo atrás à bandeira em vossa base.
Key.Korean: Find the enemy flag in Tulga and bring it back to the flag at your base.
Key.Japanese: Tulgaで敵の旗を見つけて、基地に持ち帰れ。
Key.Original: Find the enemy flag in Tulga and bring it back to the flag at your base.

Key.English: The enemy is building a prison near Pogorevka. Destroy the building so that they can not arrest innocent people.
Key.Spanish: El enemigo está construyendo una prisión cerca de Pogorevka. Destruya el edificio para que no puedan encarcelar a personas inocentes.
Key.Portuguese: O inimigo está construindo uma prisão próxima Pogorevka. Destruir o edifício de maneira que não podem prender pessoas inocentes.
Key.Korean: The enemy is building a prison near Pogorevka. Destroy the building so that they can not arrest innocent people.
Key.Japanese: 敵はPogorevka近くに刑務所を建設中だ。無実の人々を逮捕できないように建物を破壊しろ。
Key.Original: The enemy is building a prison near Pogorevka. Destroy the building so that they can not arrest innocent people.

Key.English: Good job. The prison is destroyed.
Key.Spanish: Buen trabajo. La prisión ha sido destruída.
Key.Portuguese: Trabalho bom. A prisão está destruída.
Key.Korean: Good job. The prison is destroyed.
Key.Japanese: よくやった。刑務所は破壊された。
Key.Original: Good job. The prison is destroyed.

Key.English: The enemy is producing biological weapons near Grozovoy Pass. Find the watertower that is needed for the production and destroy it.
Key.Spanish: El enemigo está produciendo armas biológicas cerca del paso Grozovoy. Encuentre el depósito de agua que se necesita para la producción y destrúyalo.
Key.Portuguese: O inimigo está produzindo as armas biológicas próximas Grozovoy Passe. Encontrar o watertower aquilo está precisado para a produção e o destruir.
Key.Korean: The enemy is producing biological weapons near Grozovoy Pass. Find the watertower that is needed for the production and destroy it.
Key.Japanese: 敵はGrozovoy Pass近くで生物兵器を製造しているようだ。これに利用されている給水塔を探して破壊しろ。
Key.Original: The enemy is producing biological weapons near Grozovoy Pass. Find the watertower that is needed for the production and destroy it.

Key.English: Good job. The water tower is down.
Key.Spanish: Buen trabajo. El depósito de agua ha sido destruído.
Key.Portuguese: Trabalho bom. A torre de água é abaixo.
Key.Korean: Good job. The water tower is down.
Key.Japanese: 給水塔は破壊された。よくやった。
Key.Original: Good job. The water tower is down.

Key.English: In the huge radio tower on top of mount Green Mountain is a IED, it looks like an ammobox. Your job is it to destroy the IED.
Key.Spanish: En la torre de radio de la parte superior del monte de Green Mountain hay un IED, se ve como una caja de munición. Su trabajo es destruir el IED.
Key.Portuguese: Na torre radiofónica enorme acima de montar a montanha Verde é um IED , parece um ammobox. Vosso trabalho é para destruir o IED.
Key.Korean: In the huge radio tower on top of mount Green Mountain is a IED, it looks like an ammobox. Your job is it to destroy the IED.
Key.Japanese: Green山の頂上にあるラジオタワーにIEDが仕掛けられた。それは大きな弾薬箱の形をしている。君の仕事はこれを破壊することだ。
Key.Original: In the huge radio tower on top of mount Green Mountain is a IED, it looks like an ammobox. Your job is it to destroy the IED.

Key.English: Good job. The IED got destroyed.
Key.Spanish: Buen trabajo. El IED fue destruído.
Key.Portuguese: Trabalho bom. O IED conseguiu destruído.
Key.Korean: Good job. The IED got destroyed.
Key.Japanese: よくやった。IEDは破壊された。
Key.Original: Good job. The IED got destroyed.

Key.English: The enemy is producing chemical weapons in a factory Solnichniy. Find the container that has some of the chemical for the production and destroy it.
Key.Spanish: El enemigo está produciendo armas químicas en una fábrica en Solnichniy. Busque el contenedor de productos químicos y destrúyalo.
Key.Portuguese: O inimigo está produzindo armas químicas em uma fábrica Solnichniy. Encontrar o contêiner que tem alguns da substância química para a produção e o destruir.
Key.Korean: The enemy is producing chemical weapons in a factory Solnichniy. Find the container that has some of the chemical for the production and destroy it.
Key.Japanese: Solnichniy工場で敵が化学兵器を製造している。製造な必要な薬品が積まれたコンテナを探して破壊しろ。
Key.Original: The enemy is producing chemical weapons in a factory Solnichniy. Find the container that has some of the chemical for the production and destroy it.

Key.English: Good job. The cargo truck is destroyed.
Key.Spanish: Buen trabajo. El camión de carga ha sido destruído.
Key.Portuguese: Trabalho bom. O cargo o caminhão está destruído.
Key.Korean: Good job. The cargo truck is destroyed.
Key.Japanese: カーゴトラックは破壊された。よくやった。
Key.Original: Good job. The cargo truck is destroyed.

Key.English: Good job. The container is destroyed.
Key.Spanish: Buen trabajo. El contenedor de productos químicos ha sido destruído.
Key.Portuguese: Trabalho bom. O contêiner está destruído.
Key.Korean: Good job. The container is destroyed.
Key.Japanese: よくやった。コンテナは破壊された。
Key.Original: Good job. The container is destroyed.

Key.English: There is a prison camp in Kumyrna. Free the prisoners and bring at least eight prisoners back to your base.
Key.Spanish: Hay un campo de prisioneros en Kumyrna. Libere los presos y lleve por lo menos ocho de ellos a su base.
Key.Portuguese: Há um acampamento para prisioneiros em Kumyrna. Livre os prisioneiros e trazer ao menos oito prisioneiros atrás a vossa base.
Key.Korean: There is a prison camp in Kumyrna. Free the prisoners and bring at least eight prisoners back to your base.
Key.Japanese: Kumyrnaで捕虜収容所を発見した。 囚人を解放し、少なくとも8人の囚人を基地に連れ帰れ。
Key.Original: There is a prison camp in Kumyrna. Free the prisoners and bring at least eight prisoners back to your base.

Key.English: Good job. The prisoners are free.
Key.Spanish: Buen trabajo. Los prisioneros han sido liberados.
Key.Portuguese: Trabalho bom. Os prisioneiros são livres.
Key.Korean: Good job. The prisoners are free.
Key.Japanese: よくやった。囚人たちは解放された。
Key.Original: Good job. The prisoners are free.

Key.English: There is a prison camp in Khelm. Free the prisoners and bring at least eight prisoners back to your base.
Key.Spanish: Hay un campo de prisioneros en Khelm. Libere los presos y lleve por lo menos ocho de ellos a su base.
Key.Portuguese: Há um acampamento para prisioneiros em Khelm. Livre os prisioneiros e trazer ao menos oito prisioneiros atrás a vossa base.
Key.Korean: There is a prison camp in Khelm. Free the prisoners and bring at least eight prisoners back to your base.
Key.Japanese: Khelmで捕虜収容所を発見した。 囚人を解放し、少なくとも8人の囚人を基地に連れ帰れ。
Key.Original: There is a prison camp in Khelm. Free the prisoners and bring at least eight prisoners back to your base.

Key.English: An enemy officer is on a walk in a forrest near Topolka-Damm. This is a good chance to arrest him and bring him to your base.
Key.Spanish: Un oficial enemigo está en camino hacia Topolka-Damm. Esta es una buena oportunidad para arrestarlo y llevarlo a su base.
Key.Portuguese: Um agente de inimigo é em um passeio em um forrest próximo Topolka-Damm. Isto é uma possibilidade boa de lhe prender e trazer a vossa base.
Key.Korean: An enemy officer is on a walk in a forrest near Topolka-Damm. This is a good chance to arrest him and bring him to your base.
Key.Japanese: Topolka-Dammの近くの森で敵の将校が散歩中だ。 これは彼を逮捕し、基地に連行するチャンスだ。
Key.Original: An enemy officer is on a walk in a forrest near Topolka-Damm. This is a good chance to arrest him and bring him to your base.

Key.English: Good job. The officer was arrested.
Key.Spanish: Buen trabajo. El oficial ha sido detenido.
Key.Portuguese: Trabalho bom. O agente esteve preso.
Key.Korean: Good job. The officer was arrested.
Key.Japanese: よくやった。将校は逮捕された。
Key.Original: Good job. The officer was arrested.

Key.English: The enemy is testing a new protoype chopper near mount Klen. Steal it and bring it to the flag at your base.
Key.Spanish: El enemigo está probando un nuevo prototipo de helicóptero cerca del monte Klen. Coja el prototipo de helicóptero y llévelo a la bandera de su base.
Key.Portuguese: O inimigo está provando um novo protoype chopper monte próximo Klen. Rouba-o e trazer à bandeira em vossa base.
Key.Korean: The enemy is testing a new protoype chopper near mount Klen. Steal it and bring it to the flag at your base.
Key.Japanese: Klen山の近くで敵が新型ヘリコプターをテスト中だ。これを盗み出して基地に持ち帰れ。
Key.Original: The enemy is testing a new protoype chopper near mount Klen. Steal it and bring it to the flag at your base.

Key.English: Good job. You got the prototype chopper.
Key.Spanish: Buen trabajo. Tiene el helicóptero prototipo.
Key.Portuguese: Trabalho bom. Conseguia o protótipo chopper
Key.Korean: Good job. You got the prototype chopper.
Key.Japanese: よくやった。新型ヘリコプターを手に入れた。
Key.Original: Good job. You got the prototype chopper.

Key.English: The enemy has all its gold in a bank in Elektrozavodsk. Destroy the building so that they can't pay their weapon shipments anymore.
Key.Spanish: El enemigo tiene todo su oro en un banco de Elektrozavodsk. Destruya el edificio de modo que no pueden pagar sus envíos de armas.
Key.Portuguese: O inimigo tem todo seu ouro em um banco em Elektrozavodsk. Destruir o edifício de maneira que não podem pagar sua arma shipments anymore
Key.Korean: The enemy has all its gold in a bank in Elektrozavodsk. Destroy the building so that they can't pay their weapon shipments anymore.
Key.Japanese: 敵はElektrozavodskにある銀行にすべての金を預けている。 建物を破壊して、これ以上兵器の輸入をできないようにしろ。
Key.Original: The enemy has all its gold in a bank in Elektrozavodsk. Destroy the building so that they can't pay their weapon shipments anymore.

Key.English: Good job. The bank building is down.
Key.Spanish: Buen trabajo. El edificio del banco ha sido destruído.
Key.Portuguese: Trabalho bom. O edifício de banco é abaixo.
Key.Korean: Good job. The bank building is down.
Key.Japanese: よくやった。銀行は破壊された。
Key.Original: Good job. The bank building is down.

Key.English: The enemy is producing ball bearings in a factory in Chernogorsk. Destroy the main building and the two chimneys to stop the production.
Key.Spanish: El enemigo tiene una fábrica de producción de bolas de rodamientos en Chernogorsk. Destruya el edificio principal y las dos chimeneas para detener la producción.
Key.Portuguese: The enemy is producing ball bearings in a factory in Chernogorsk. Destroy the main building and the two chimneys to stop the production.
Key.Korean: The enemy is producing ball bearings in a factory in Chernogorsk. Destroy the main building and the two chimneys to stop the production.
Key.Japanese: 敵はChernogorskの工場でボールベアリングを生産している。 主要建物と2つの煙突を破壊して生産を停止させろ。
Key.Original: The enemy is producing ball bearings in a factory in Chernogorsk. Destroy the main building and the two chimneys to stop the production.

Key.English: Good job. The factory is down.
Key.Spanish: Buen trabajo. La fábrica ha sido destruída.
Key.Portuguese: Trabalho bom. A fábrica é abaixo.
Key.Korean: Good job. The factory is down.
Key.Japanese: よくやった。工場は破壊された。
Key.Original: Good job. The factory is down.

Key.English: The enemy is producing ammunition in a factory near Berezino. Destroy the main building and the pipelines to stop the production.
Key.Spanish: El enemigo esta produciendo municiones en una fábrica cerca de Berezino. Destruir el edificio principal y los oleoductos para detener la producción.
Key.Portuguese: O inimigo está produzindo munição em uma fábrica próxima Berezino. Destruir o edifício principal e os encanamentos para parar a produção.
Key.Korean: The enemy is producing ammunition in a factory near Berezino. Destroy the main building and the pipelines to stop the production.
Key.Japanese: 敵はBerezino近くの工場で弾薬を生産している。 主要建物とパイプラインを破壊して生産を停止させろ。
Key.Original: The enemy is producing ammunition in a factory near Berezino. Destroy the main building and the pipelines to stop the production.

Key.English: There is a huge transformer station near Zelenogorsk. Destroy the three transfomers to cut down the electrical power.
Key.Spanish: Hay una estación de transformadores enorme cerca Zelenogorsk. Destruya los tres transformadores para reducir la energía eléctrica.
Key.Portuguese: Há uma estação de transformador enorme próximo Zelenogorsk. Destruir o três transfomers para cortar abaixo o poder elétrico.
Key.Korean: There is a huge transformer station near Zelenogorsk. Destroy the three transfomers to cut down the electrical power.
Key.Japanese: Zelenogorskの近くには大きな変電所がある。 3つの変電器を破壊して電力をとめろ。
Key.Original: There is a huge transformer station near Zelenogorsk. Destroy the three transfomers to cut down the electrical power.

Key.English: Good job. The transformer station is destroyed.
Key.Spanish: Buen trabajo. La estación de transformadores han sido destruída.
Key.Portuguese: Trabalho bom. A estação de transformador está destruída.
Key.Korean: Good job. The transformer station is destroyed.
Key.Japanese: よくやった。変電所は破壊された。
Key.Original: Good job. The transformer station is destroyed.

Key.English: The enemy has a small outpost in a valley near Staroye. Arrest the officer there and bring him back to the flag at your base to get some vital informations.
Key.Spanish: El enemigo tiene un pequeño puesto de avanzada en un valle cercano a Staroye. Arrestar al oficial y llevarlo a la bandera de la base para obtener alguna información esencial.
Key.Portuguese: O inimigo tem um pequeno outpost em um vale próximo Staroye. Prendo o agente ali e trazer-lhe atrás à bandeira em vossa base para conseguir algumas informações vitais.
Key.Korean: The enemy has a small outpost in a valley near Staroye. Arrest the officer there and bring him back to the flag at your base to get some vital informations.
Key.Japanese: 敵はStaroye近くの谷に小さな前哨基地を構えている。 重要な情報を入手するため、そこで将校を逮捕し、基地に連行しろ。
Key.Original: The enemy has a small outpost in a valley near Staroye. Arrest the officer there and bring him back to the flag at your base to get some vital informations.

Key.English: Good job. The officer was arrested.
Key.Spanish: Buen trabajo. El oficial ha sido detenido.
Key.Portuguese: Trabalho bom. O agente esteve preso.
Key.Korean: Good job. The officer was arrested.
Key.Japanese: よくやった。将校は逮捕された。
Key.Original: Good job. The officer was arrested.

Key.English: Intel reports about a train with vital military equipment leaving Chernogorsk habour soon. Find the train and destroy it!
Key.Spanish: El servicio de inteligencia informa acerca de un tren con un equipo vital militar que dejará pronto Chernogorsk. ¡Encuentre el tren y destrúyalo!
Key.Portuguese: Intel Relatórios sobre um trem com o equipamento militar vital que deixa Chernogorsk habour cedo. Encontrar o trem e destruí-lo!
Key.Korean: Intel reports about a train with vital military equipment leaving Chernogorsk habour soon. Find the train and destroy it!
Key.Japanese: 情報部がChernogorsk港をすぐに出発する重要な軍用機材を備えた電車について報告している。 電車を見つけてそれを破壊しろ！
Key.Original: Intel reports about a train with vital military equipment leaving Chernogorsk habour soon. Find the train and destroy it!

Key.English: Good job. All artillery guns are down. No artillery observers will appear at main targets anymore.
Key.Spanish: Buen trabajo. Todas las piezas de artillería están destruídas. No aparecerán más observadores de artillería en los objetivos principales.
Key.Portuguese: Trabalho bom. Todas pistolas de artilharia são abaixo. Nenhum observadores de artilharia aparecerão em objetivos principais anymore.
Key.Korean: Good job. All artillery guns are down. No artillery observers will appear at main targets anymore.
Key.Japanese: よくやった。すべての敵長距離砲を破壊した。砲兵観測手がメインターゲットに現れることはもうないだろう。
Key.Original: Good job. All artillery guns are down. No artillery observers will appear at main targets anymore.

Key.English: One of our own choppers was shot down near Gorka. Find and rescue the crew and bring them back to base. Attention, enemy units are also on the way to the chopper. You have about 15 minutes before they arrive.
Key.Spanish: Uno de nuestros helicópteros fue derribado cerca de Gorka. Busque y rescate a la tripulación y llévelos de vuelta a la base. Atención, las unidades enemigas también están en camino hacia el helicóptero. Tiene 15 minutos antes de que lleguen.
Key.Portuguese: Um de nosso próprio choppers esteve disparado abaixo Gorka próximo. Encontra e resgatar a tripulação e trazer-lhes atrás para basear. Atenção, unidades de inimigo são também no caminho ao chopper. Tem aproximadamente 15 minutos dantes de que chegam.
Key.Korean: One of our own choppers was shot down near Gorka. Find and rescue the crew and bring them back to base. Attention, enemy units are also on the way to the chopper. You have about 15 minutes before they arrive.
Key.Japanese: 我が軍のヘリコプターがGorkaの近くで撃墜された。クルーを救出し基地に連れ帰れ。気を付けろ、敵軍もそこに向かっている。15分程度で到着するだろう。
Key.Original: One of our own choppers was shot down near Gorka. Find and rescue the crew and bring them back to base. Attention, enemy units are also on the way to the chopper. You have about 15 minutes before they arrive.

Key.English: Good job. The crew is back at base.
Key.Spanish: Buen trabajo. La tripulación está de vuelta en la base.
Key.Portuguese: Trabalho bom. A tripulação está de volta em base.
Key.Korean: Good job. The crew is back at base.
Key.Japanese: よくやった。クルーは無事基地に戻った。
Key.Original: Good job. The crew is back at base.

Key.English: One of our own choppers %1. Find and rescue the crew and bring them back to base. Attention, enemy units are also on the way to the chopper. You have about 15 minutes before they arrive.

Key.English: The enemy is building a hangar near Zelegonorsk. Funny thing is, there is no airfield near that position. So, destroy that hangar before we really know what it is for.
Key.Spanish: El enemigo ha construido un hangar cerca de Zelegonorsk. Lo curioso es que no hay base aérea cerca de esa posición. Por lo tanto, destruya ese hangar antes de que realmente sepamos para que és.
Key.Portuguese: O inimigo está construindo um hangar próximo Zelegonorsk. A coisa graciosa é, não há nenhum aeródromo próximo que posição. Tão, destrói que hangar dantes de que realmente sabemos que é para.
Key.Korean: The enemy is building a hangar near Zelegonorsk. Funny thing is, there is no airfield near that position. So, destroy that hangar before we really know what it is for
Key.Japanese: Zelegonorskの近くに敵が格納庫を建設中だが、おかしなことにその近くに飛行場はない。何に使われるか判明する前に破壊しろ。
Key.Original: The enemy is building a hangar near Zelegonorsk. Funny thing is, there is no airfield near that position. So, destroy that hangar before we really know what it is for.

Key.English: Good job. The hangar is down.
Key.Spanish: Buen trabajo. El hangar ha sido destruído.
Key.Portuguese: Trabalho bom. O hangar é abaixo.
Key.Korean: Good job. The hangar is down.
Key.Japanese: よくやった。格納庫は破壊された。
Key.Original: Good job. The hangar is down.

Key.Japanese: Ifestionaに敵訓練施設がある。新しい兵士を訓練する可能性を減らすために主要な建物を破壊しろ。
Key.Original: There is an enemy training facility near Ifestiona. Destroy the main building to cut down their possibilities to train new soldiers.

Key.Original: An enemy officer is on a walk in a forrest near Nur. This is a good chance to arrest him and bring him to your base.

Key.English: An enemy officer is on a walk in a forrest near Air Station Mike-26. This is a good chance to arrest him and bring him to your base.
Key.Spanish: Un oficial enemigo está en una caminata en un bosque cerca de la estación aérea Mike-26. Esta es una buena oportunidad para arrestarlo y llevarlo a su base.
Key.Portuguese: Um agente de inimigo é em um passeio em um forrest Estação de Ar próximo Mike-26. Isto é uma possibilidade boa de lhe prender e trazer a vossa base.

Key.English: The enemy is testing a new protoype chopper at Almyra. Steal it and bring it to the map at your base.
Key.Spanish: El enemigo está probando un nuevo prototipo de helicóptero en Almyra. Róbelo y llévelo al mapa de su base.

Key.Original: The enemy is testing a new protoype chopper at Almyra. Steal it and bring it to the map at your base.

Key.English: The enemy is testing a new protoype chopper near Zavarak. Steal it and bring it to the flag at your base.
Key.Spanish: El enemigo está probando un nuevo prototipo de helicóptero cerca de Zavarak. Coja el prototipo de helicóptero y llévelo a la bandera de su base.
Key.Portuguese: O inimigo está provando um novo protoype chopper próximo Zavarak. Rouba-o e trazer à bandeira em vossa base.

Key.Original: The enemy is testing a new protoype chopper near Zavarak. Steal it and bring it to the flag at your base.

Key.English: The enemy is testing a new protoype chopper at Strogos Bay. Steal it and bring it to the flag at your base.

Key.Korean: The enemy is producing ball bearings in a power plant near Sofia. Destroy the fuel tanks to stop the production.
Key.Japanese: 敵はSofia付近の工場でボールベアリングを生産している。 燃料タンクを破壊して生産を停止させろ。
Key.Original: The enemy is producing ball bearings in a power plant near Sofia. Destroy the fuel tanks to stop the production.

Key.English: Good job. The fuel tanks are down.
Key.Spanish: Buen trabajo. Los tanques de combustible han sido destruídos.
Key.Portuguese: Trabalho bom. Os tanques de combustível são abaixo.
Key.Korean: Trabalho bom. Os tanques de combustível são abaixo.
Key.Japanese: よくやった。燃料タンクは破壊された。
Key.Original: Good job. The fuel tanks are down.

Key.English: The enemy has a power plant near Aggelochori. Destroy the huge tanks there to cut down the enemy fuel supplies.
Key.Spanish: El enemigo tiene una planta de energía cerca Aggelochori. Destruya los enormes tanques de allí, para cortar los suministros de combustible del enemigo.
Key.Portuguese: O inimigo tem uma planta de poder próxima Aggelochori. Destruir os tanques enormes ali para cortar abaixo os fornecimentos de combustível do inimigo.
Key.Korean: The enemy has a power plant near Aggelochori. Destroy the huge tanks there to cut down the enemy fuel supplies.
Key.Japanese: 敵はAggelochori近くの発電所を持っている。 そこにある巨大な燃料タンクを破壊して、敵の燃料を削れ。
Key.Original: The enemy has a power plant near Aggelochori. Destroy the huge tanks there to cut down the enemy fuel supplies.

Key.English: The enemy has some very productive oil pumps near Nagara-1-Oilfield. Destroy the pumps there to cut down the enemy fuel supllies.
Key.Spanish: El enemigo tiene algunas bombas de petróleo muy productiva cerca de Nagara-1-Oilfield. Destruya las bombas para reducir el combustible.
Key.Portuguese: O inimigo tem algum azeite muito produtivo bombea próximo Nagara-1-Oilfield. Destruir as bombas ali para cortar abaixo o combustível de inimigo supllies.
Key.Korean: The enemy has some very productive oil pumps near Nagara-1-Oilfield. Destroy the pumps there to cut down the enemy fuel supllies.
Key.Japanese: 敵はNagara-1-油田の近くに非常に優良なオイルポンプをいくつか持っています。 敵の燃料供給を減らすためにそこにあるポンプを破壊しろ。
Key.Original: The enemy has some very productive oil pumps near Nagara-1-Oilfield. Destroy the pumps there to cut down the enemy fuel supllies.

Key.English: Good job. The oil pumps are down.
Key.Spanish: Buen trabajo. Las bombas de petróleo están destruídas.
Key.Portuguese: Trabalho bom. As bombas de azeite são abaixo.
Key.Korean: Good job. The oil pumps are down.
Key.Japanese: よくやった。 オイルポンプは停止した。
Key.Original: Good job. The oil pumps are down.

Key.English: The enemy has a small outpost on the south island. Arrest the officer there and bring him back to the map at your base to get some vital informations.
Key.Spanish: El enemigo tiene un pequeño puesto de avanzada al sur de la isla. Detenga al oficial enemigo y llévelo de vuelta al mapa de su base para conseguir información vital.
Key.Portuguese: O inimigo tem um pequeno outpost na ilha do sul. Prendo o agente ali e trazer-lhe atrás ao mapa em vossa base para conseguir algumas informações vitais.
Key.Korean: The enemy has a small outpost on the south island. Arrest the officer there and bring him back to the map at your base to get some vital informations.
Key.Japanese: 敵は南の島に小さな前哨基地を持っています。 重要な情報を入手するため、そこで将校を逮捕し、基地に連行しろ。
Key.Original: The enemy has a small outpost on the south island. Arrest the officer there and bring him back to the map at your base to get some vital informations.

Key.English: The enemy has a small outpost in a valley near Jilavur. Arrest the officer there and bring him back to the flag at your base to get some vital informations.
Key.Spanish: El enemigo tiene un pequeño puesto de avanzada en un valle cercano a Jilavur. Arrestar al oficial y llevarlo a la bandera de la base para obtener alguna información esencial.
Key.Portuguese: O inimigo tem um pequeno outpost em um vale próximo Jilavur. Prendo o agente ali e trazer-lhe atrás à bandeira em vossa base para conseguir algumas informações vitais.
Key.Korean: The enemy has a small outpost in a valley near Jilavur. Arrest the officer there and bring him back to the flag at your base to get some vital informations.
Key.Japanese: 敵はJilavur近郊の村に小さな前哨基地を持っています。 重要な情報を入手するため、そこで将校を逮捕し、基地に連行しろ。
Key.Original: The enemy has a small outpost in a valley near Jilavur. Arrest the officer there and bring him back to the flag at your base to get some vital informations.

Key.English: The enemy has a uran mine near Charkia. Your task: destroy the transformer to prevent further mining!
Key.Spanish: El enemigo tiene una mina cerca de Charkia. Su tarea: Destruya el transformador para evitar una mayor minera.
Key.Portuguese: O inimigo tem um uran a mina próxima Charkia. Vossa tarefa: destruir o transformador para impedir mais longínquo mineiro!
Key.Korean: The enemy has a uran mine near Charkia. Your task: destroy the transformer to prevent further mining!
Key.Japanese: 敵はCharkiaの近くにウラン鉱山を持ってる。 ミッション：さらなる鉱業を防ぐために変電器を破壊する！
Key.Original: The enemy has a uran mine near Charkia. Your task: destroy the transformer to prevent further mining!

Key.English: The enemy has a uran mine near Feruz-Abad. Your task: destroy the containers with mining equipment to prevent further mining!
Key.Spanish: El enemigo tiene una mina de uranio cerca de Feruz-Abad. Su tarea es destruir los contenedores con equipo de minería.
Key.Portuguese: O inimigo tem um uran a mina próxima Feruz-Abad. Vossa tarefa: destruir os contêiners com equipamento mineiro para impedir mais longínquo mineiro!
Key.Korean: The enemy has a uran mine near Feruz-Abad. Your task: destroy the containers with mining equipment to prevent further mining!
Key.Japanese: 敵はFeruz-Abadの近くにウラン鉱山を持ってる。ミッション：さらなる鉱業を防ぐために採掘設備を破壊する！
Key.Original: The enemy has a uran mine near Feruz-Abad. Your task: destroy the containers with mining equipment to prevent further mining!

Key.English: Good job. You have destroyed the transformer.
Key.Spanish: Buen trabajo. Ha destruído el transformador.
Key.Portuguese: Trabalho bom. Tem destruído o transformador.
Key.Korean: Good job. You have destroyed the transformer.
Key.Japanese: よくやった。変電器は破壊された
Key.Original: Good job. You have destroyed the transformer.

Key.English: Good job. You have destroyed the containers.
Key.Spanish: Buen trabajo. Los contenedores han sido destruídos.
Key.Portuguese: Trabalho bom. Tem destruído os contêiners.
Key.Korean: Good job. You have destroyed the containers.
Key.Japanese: よくやった。コンテナは破壊された
Key.Original: Good job. You have destroyed the containers.

Key.English: was shot down near Abdera
Key.Spanish: fue derribado cerca de Abdera
Key.Portuguese: Esteve disparado abaixo próximo Abdera
Key.Japanese: Abdera付近で撃墜された。
Key.Original: was shot down near Abdera

Key.English: One of our own choppers was shot down near Chaman. Find and rescue the crew and bring them back to base. Attention, enemy units are also on the way to the chopper. You have about 15 minutes before they arrive.
Key.Spanish: Uno de nuestros helicópteros fue derribado cerca de Chaman. Busque y rescate a la tripulación y llévelos de vuelta a la base. Atención, las unidades enemigas también están en camino hacia el helicóptero. Tiene 15 minutos antes de que lleguen.
Key.Portuguese: Um de nosso próprio choppers esteve disparado abaixo próximo Chaman. Encontra e resgatar a tripulação e trazer-lhes atrás para basear. Atenção, unidades de inimigo são também no caminho ao chopper. Tem aproximadamente 15 minutos dantes de que chegam.
Key.Korean: One of our own choppers was shot down near Chaman. Find and rescue the crew and bring them back to base. Attention, enemy units are also on the way to the chopper. You have about 15 minutes before they arrive.
Key.Japanese: 我が軍のヘリコプターがChaman付近で撃墜された。クルーを救出し基地に連れ帰れ。気を付けろ、敵軍もそこに向かっている。15分程度で到着するだろう。
Key.Original: One of our own choppers was shot down near Chaman. Find and rescue the crew and bring them back to base. Attention, enemy units are also on the way to the chopper. You have about 15 minutes before they arrive.

Key.English: The enemy is building a hangar at the research base nr Agios Georgios. There is no airfield near that position. So, destroy that hangar before we really know what it is for.
Key.Spanish: El enemigo está construyendo un hangar en la base de investigación cerca de Agios Georgios. No hay campo de aviación cerca de esa posición. Por lo tanto, destruya ese hangar antes de que realmente sepamos para que es.
Key.Portuguese: O inimigo está construindo um hangar na base de busca nr Agios Georgios. não há nenhum aeródromo próximo que posição. Tão, destrói que hangar dantes de que realmente sabemos que é para.
Key.Korean: The enemy is building a hangar at the research base nr Agios Georgios. There is no airfield near that position. So, destroy that hangar before we really know what it is for.
Key.Japanese: Agios Georgios近郊の研究拠点付近に敵が格納庫を建設中だ。その近くに飛行場はない。何に使われるか判明する前に破壊しろ。
Key.Original: The enemy is building a hangar at the research base nr Agios Georgios. There is no airfield near that position. So, destroy that hangar before we really know what it is for.

Key.English: The enemy is building a hangar near Falar. Funny thing is, there is no airfield near that position. So, destroy that hangar before we really know what it is for.

Key.Portuguese: O inimigo está construindo um hangar próximo Falar. A coisa graciosa é, não há nenhum aeródromo próximo que posição. Tão, destrói que hangar dantes de que realmente sabemos que é para.

Key.English: There is a radio tower on the island Makrynisi. The enemy uses it to communicate. Simple task, destroy it.
Key.Spanish: Hay una torre de radio en la isla Makrynisi. El enemigo la usa para comunicarse. Tarea sencilla, destrúyala.
Key.Portuguese: Há uma torre radiofónica na ilha Makrynisi. Ou inimigo utiliza-ou para comunicar. Tarefa singela, destruí-o.
Key.Korean: There is a radio tower on the island Makrynisi. The enemy uses it to communicate. Simple task, destroy it.
Key.Japanese: Makrynisi島にラジオタワーがある。敵はこれを通信に利用しているようだ。それを破壊しろ。
Key.Original: There is a radio tower on the island Makrynisi. The enemy uses it to communicate. Simple task, destroy it.

Key.Portuguese: Há uma torre radiofónica na parte superior de uma montanha próxima Landay. O inimigo utiliza-o para comunicar. Tarefa singela, destruí-lo.
Key.Korean: There is a radio tower on the top of a mountain near Landay. The enemy uses it to communicate. Simple task, destroy it.
Key.Japanese: Landay付近の山の頂上にラジオタワーがある。敵はこれを通信に利用している。それを破壊しろ。

Key.English: A new helicopter prototype gets tested near Selakano. Destroy it before enemy troops use it.
Key.Spanish: Un nuevo prototipo de helicóptero está haciendo pruebas cerca de Selakano. Destrúyalo antes de que las tropas enemigas lo utilice.
Key.Portuguese: Um protótipo de helicóptero novo consegue provado próximo Selakano. Destrói-o dantes de que tropas de inimigo o utilizam.
Key.Korean: A new helicopter prototype gets tested near Selakano. Destroy it before enemy troops use it.
Key.Japanese: Selakanoの近くで敵が新型ヘリコプターをテスト中だ。敵軍が使用する前に破壊しろ。
Key.Original: A new helicopter prototype gets tested near Selakano. Destroy it before enemy troops use it.

Key.English: A new helicopter prototype gets tested on Rasman airfield. Destroy it before enemy troops use it.
Key.Spanish: Un nuevo prototipo de helicóptero está haciendo pruebas en el aeródromo de Rasman. Destruya el prototipo de helicóptero antes de que las tropas enemigas lo utilicen.
Key.Portuguese: Um protótipo de helicóptero novo consegue provado em Rasman aeródromo. Destrói-o dantes de que tropas de inimigo o utilizam.
Key.Korean: A new helicopter prototype gets tested on Rasman airfield. Destroy it before enemy troops use it.
Key.Japanese: Rasman飛行場で敵が新型ヘリコプターをテスト中だ。敵軍が使用する前に破壊しろ。
Key.Original: A new helicopter prototype gets tested on Rasman airfield. Destroy it before enemy troops use it.

Key.English: A new helicopter prototype gets tested near Kamino Firing-Range. Destroy it before enemy troops use it.

Key.Portuguese: Todos observadores de artilharia do inimigo abaixo em objetivo principal atual
Key.Korean: 현 지역내 모든 포병 감적수들이 무력화 되었습니다.
Key.Japanese: メインターゲットの砲兵観測手は全て無力化された
Key.Original: All enemy artillery observers down at current main target

Key.English: Radio tower spotted at main target. Destroy it so that the enemy can not call in airborne reinforcements.
Key.Spanish: Torre de radio colocada en el objetivo principal. Destrúyala para que el enemigo no pueda pedir refuerzos.
Key.Portuguese: Torre radiofónica spotted em objetivo principal. Destrói-o de maneira que o inimigo não pode chamar em airborne reforços.
Key.Korean: 작전지역내에 통신탑이 발견되었습니다. 파괴하여 추가적인 증원요청을 막으십시오
Key.Japanese: メインターゲットにラジオタワーを発見。これを破壊し、敵の援軍要請を妨害しろ。
Key.Original: Radio tower spotted at main target. Destroy it so that the enemy can not call in airborne reinforcements.

Key.English: Main target radio tower down. Now the enemy will not be able to call in further reinforcements.
Key.Spanish: La torre de radio ha sido destruída. Ahora el enemigo no será capaz de pedir más refuerzos.
Key.Portuguese: Objetivo principal torre radiofónica abaixo. Agora o inimigo não será capaz de chamar em reforços mais longínquos.
Key.Korean: 작전지역내에 있던 통신탑이 파괴되었음으로 더이상 증원이 오지않습니다.
Key.Japanese: メインターゲットのラジオタワーは破壊された。敵はこれ以上援軍を呼ぶことはできないだろう。
Key.Original: Main target radio tower down. Now the enemy will not be able to call in further reinforcements.

Key.English: %1 enemy camps sighted at main target... capture them all!!!
Key.Spanish: %1 campamentos enemigos avistadas en el objetivo principal... Captúrelos todos.
Key.Portuguese: %1 acampamentos de inimigo sighted em objetivo principal... Captura-lhes tudo!!!
Key.Japanese: メインターゲットに%1か所のキャンプを発見...すべて占領しろ!!!
Key.Original: %1 enemy camps sighted at main target... capture them all!!!

Key.English: The enemy has spotted you at main target... They will now call in reinforcements!!!
Key.Spanish: El enemigo tiene puntos de referencia de su equipo en la misión principal... Ellos pedirán refuerzos.
Key.Portuguese: O inimigo tem spotted você em objetivo principal... Eles agora chamada em reforços!!!
Key.Korean: 적이 당신의 위치를 파악했습니다. 곧 적 증원이 급파됩니다!
Key.Japanese: メインターゲットで敵に発見された...敵が増援を要請!!!
Key.Original: The enemy has spotted you at main target... They will now call in reinforcements!!!

Key.English: The enemy has spotted one of the teams at main target... They will now call in reinforcements!!!
Key.Spanish: El enemigo tiene puntos de referencia de su equipo en la misión principal... ¡Ellos pedirán refuerzos!
Key.Portuguese: O inimigo tem spotted um das equipes em objetivo principal... Eles agora chamada em reforços!!!
Key.Korean: 적이 아군의 위치를 파악했습니다. 곧 적이 증원을 요청합니다.
Key.Japanese: メインターゲットで味方チームが敵に発見された...敵が増援を要請!!!
Key.Original: The enemy has spotted one of the teams at main target... They will now call in reinforcements!!!

Key.English: All side missions resolved!
Key.Spanish: Todas las misiones secundarias han sido resueltas.
Key.Portuguese: Todas missões de lado resolveram!
Key.Japanese: すべてのサイドミッションを解決!!!
Key.Original: All side missions resolved!

Key.English: It seems that the enemy doesn't want to give up %1 and starts a counterattack. Search defensive positions, the attack will start in a few minutes...
Key.Spanish: Parece que el enemigo no quiere renunciar a %1 e inicia un contra-ataque. Busque una posiciones defensiva, el ataque comenzará en unos minutos...
Key.Portuguese: Parece que o inimigo não quer deixar %1 e começa um contraataque. Busca posicione defensivas, o ataque começará em uns quantos minutos...
Key.Korean: 후퇴하였던 적이 전열을 재정비하고 %1 지역으로 반격을 준비하고있습니다. 엄폐물을 찾고 방어전을 준비하십시오.
Key.Japanese: 敵は%1をあきらめず、反撃をするようだ。遮蔽物を探し防衛に努めよ。
Key.Original: It seems that the enemy doesn't want to give up %1 and starts a counterattack. Search defensive positions, the attack will start in a few minutes...

Key.English: The counterattack starts. Hold the current target. Good luck and god help us all...
Key.Spanish: El contra-ataque comienza. Defienda la posición. Buena suerte a todos...
Key.Portuguese: Os inícios de contraataque. Controle o objetivo atual. Deus e sorte bons ajudamos-nos tudo...
Key.Japanese: 敵の反撃が始まった。各自メインターゲットを死守せよ。幸運を...
Key.Original: The counterattack starts. Hold the current target. Good luck and god help us all...

Key.English: Good job. The counterattack was defeated.
Key.Spanish: Buen trabajo muchachos. Contra-ataque fallido.
Key.Portuguese: Trabalho bom. O contraataque esteve derrotado.
Key.Japanese: よくやった、敵の反撃を退けた。
Key.Original: Good job. The counterattack was defeated.

Key.English: %1 gets transported by airlift
Key.Spanish: %1 es transportado por aire
Key.Portuguese: %1 consegue transportado por ponte aérea
Key.Japanese: %1を空輸中
Key.Original: %1 gets transported by airlift

Key.Spanish: ¡¡¡ %1 está disponible de nuevo !!! Don't forget to deploy the MHQ!!!!!
Key.Portuguese: %1 é disponível outra vez !!! Não esquece para despregar o MHQ!!!!!

Key.Original: %1 is available again !!! Don't forget to deploy the MHQ!!!!!

Key.Japanese: キャンプをBluforが占領した!
Key.Original: Camp captured by Blufor troops!

Key.Japanese: キャンプを独立軍が占領した!
Key.Original: Camp captured by Independent troops!
