Key.English: There is a radar tower on the top of mount Pico de Perez. Find it and destroy it.
Key.Spanish: Hay una torre de radar en la cima del monte Pico de Pérez. Buscarla y destruirla.
Key.Portuguese: Há uma torre de radar na parte superior de monte Pico de Perez. Encontra-o e destruí-lo.
Key.Korean: Pico de Perez 산 정상에 레디어 기지가 있다는 첩보입니다. 찾아서 파괴하십시오.
Key.Japanese: Pico de Perez山の頂上にレーダータワーがある。探して破壊しろ。
Key.Original: There is a radar tower on the top of mount Pico de Perez. Find it and destroy it.

Key.English: A high enemy officer arrives today in a ruin south of Tres Valles. He is responsible for the death of many civilians. Eliminate him!
Key.Spanish: Un alto oficial enemigo llega hoy a una ruina al sur de Tres Valles. Es el responsable de la muerte de muchos civiles. Elimínelo.
Key.Portuguese: Um agente de inimigo alto chega hoje em um sul de ruína de Três Vales. É responsável para a morte de muitos civis. Elimina-lhe!
Key.Korean: A high enemy officer arrives today in a ruin south of Tres Valles. He is responsible for the death of many civilians. Eliminate him!
Key.Japanese: 敵高級将校が今日Tresの南の廃墟に到着する。彼は多くの民間人の死に関与している。彼を排除しろ!
Key.Original: A high enemy officer arrives today in a ruin south of Tres Valles. He is responsible for the death of many civilians. Eliminate him!

Key.English: There is a artillery cannon on top of mount San Esteban. Destroy it before enemy troops use it to attack Ortego.
Key.Spanish: Hay un cañón de artillería en la cima del monte de San Esteban. Destrúyalo antes de que las tropas enemigas lo utilicen para atacar Ortego.
Key.Portuguese: Há um canhão de artilharia acima de monte San Esteban. Destrói-o dantes de que tropas de inimigo o utilizam para atacar Ortego.
Key.Korean: There is a artillery cannon on top of mount San Esteban. Destroy it before enemy troops use it to attack Ortego.
Key.Japanese: San Esteban山の頂上に長距離砲がある。敵がこれを使ってOrtegoを攻撃する前に破壊しろ
Key.Original: There is a artillery cannon on top of mount San Esteban. Destroy it before enemy troops use it to attack Ortego.

Key.English: There is a lighthouse on Isla del Zorra. Enemy ships use it to find their way to the Sahrani south coast, destroy it.
Key.Spanish: Hay un faro en la Isla de la Zorra. Los barcos enemigos lo utilizan para encontrar su camino a la costa sur de Sahrani, destrúyalo.
Key.Portuguese: Há um faro em Ilha do Zorra. Barcos de inimigo utilizam-no para encontrar sua maneira ao Sahrani costa do sul, destruí-lo.
Key.Korean: There is a lighthouse on Isla del Zorra. Enemy ships use it to find their way to the Sahrani south coast, destroy it.
Key.Japanese: del Zorra島に灯台がある。敵の船はそれを使ってSahraniの南岸に向かっている、それを破壊しろ。
Key.Original: There is a lighthouse on Isla del Zorra. Enemy ships use it to find their way to the Sahrani south coast, destroy it.

Key.English: Good job. The lighthouse is destroyed.
Key.Spanish: Buen trabajo. El faro ha sido destruido.
Key.Portuguese: Trabalho bom. O faro está destruído.
Key.Korean: Good job. The lighthouse is destroyed.
Key.Japanese: よくやった。灯台は破壊された。
Key.Original: Good job. The lighthouse is destroyed.

Key.English: A high enemy officer makes holidays at Cabo Canino. Eliminate him!
Key.Spanish: Un alto oficial enemigo está de vacaciones en el Cabo Canino. Elimínelo.
Key.Portuguese: Umas marcas de agente de inimigo altas férias em Cabo Canino. Elimina-lhe!
Key.Korean: A high enemy officer makes holidays at Cabo Canino. Eliminate him!
Key.Japanese: 敵高級将校がCabo Caninoで休暇を過ごしている。彼を排除しろ!
Key.Original: A high enemy officer makes holidays at Cabo Canino. Eliminate him!

Key.English: The North prime minister visits some troops in Valle Azul. Eliminate him!
Key.Spanish: El primer ministro Norte visita a algunas tropas en el Valle Azul. Elimínelo.
Key.Portuguese: As visitas de premiê Do norte algumas tropas em Vale Azul. Elimina-lhe!
Key.Korean: The North prime minister visits some troops in Valle Azul. Eliminate him!
Key.Japanese: 北の首相がValle Azulの部隊を訪問する。彼を排除しろ!
Key.Original: The North prime minister visits some troops in Valle Azul. Eliminate him!

Key.English: There is a radio tower on the top of mount Monte Liberacion. The enemy uses it to command its armored troops. Simple task, destroy it.
Key.Spanish: Hay una torre de radio en la cima del Monte Liberación. El enemigo lo usa para comandar sus tropas blindadas. Tarea sencilla, destrúyala.
Key.Portuguese: Há uma torre radiofónica na parte superior de monte Monte Liberacion. O inimigo utiliza-o para mandar suas tropas blindadas. Tarefa singela, destruí-lo.
Key.Korean: There is a radio tower on the top of mount Monte Liberacion. The enemy uses it to command its armored troops. Simple task, destroy it.
Key.Japanese: Liberacion山の頂上にラジオタワーがある。敵はこれを装甲車両隊の指揮に利用してるようだ。それを破壊しろ。
Key.Original: There is a radio tower on the top of mount Monte Liberacion. The enemy uses it to command its armored troops. Simple task, destroy it.

Key.English: There is a transformer station in Tlaloc. The enemy uses it to for some experiments in a laboratory in Bagango. Simple task, destroy it.
Key.Spanish: Hay un centro de transformación en Tlaloc. El enemigo lo utiliza para algunos experimentos en un laboratorio en Bagango. Tarea sencilla, destrúyalo.
Key.Portuguese: Há uma estação de transformador em Tlaloc. O inimigo utiliza-o a para alguns experimentos em um laboratório em Bagango. Tarefa singela, destruí-lo.
Key.Korean: There is a transformer station in Tlaloc. The enemy uses it to for some experiments in a laboratory in Bagango. Simple task, destroy it.
Key.Japanese: Tlalocに変電所がある。敵はBagangoの研究所での実験に利用しているようだ。簡単な任務だ、それを破壊しろ。
Key.Original: There is a transformer station in Tlaloc. The enemy uses it to for some experiments in a laboratory in Bagango. Simple task, destroy it.

Key.English: There is a radio tower on the top of a mountain south of Cabo Valiente. The enemy uses it to command its marine task forces. Simple task, destroy it.
Key.Spanish: Hay una torre de radio en la cima de una montaña al sur del Cabo Valiente. El enemigo la usa para mandar sus equipos de tareas marinas. Tarea sencilla, destrúyala.
Key.Portuguese: Há uma torre radiofónica na parte superior de um sul de montanha de Cabo Valente. O inimigo utiliza-o para mandar suas forças de tarefa marinhas. Tarefa singela, destruí-lo.
Key.Korean: There is a radio tower on the top of a mountain south of Cabo Valiente. The enemy uses it to command its marine task forces. Simple task, destroy it.
Key.Japanese: Cabo Valiente山の頂上にラジオタワーがある。敵はこれを海上タスクフォースの指揮に利用してるようだ。それを破壊しろ。
Key.Original: There is a radio tower on the top of a mountain south of Cabo Valiente. The enemy uses it to command its marine task forces. Simple task, destroy it.

Key.English: A high enemy officer arrives today in Valor. He is responsible for the production of biological and chemical weapons. Eliminate him!
Key.Spanish: Un alto oficial enemigo llega hoy a Valor. Es el responsable de la producción de armas biológicas y químicas. Elimínelo.
Key.Portuguese: Um agente de inimigo alto chega hoje em Valor. É responsável para a produção de biológico e armas químicas. Elimina-lhe!
Key.Korean: A high enemy officer arrives today in Valor. He is responsible for the production of biological and chemical weapons. Eliminate him!
Key.Japanese: 敵高級将校が今日Valorに到着する。彼は生物化学兵器の製造に関与している。彼を排除しろ!
Key.Original: A high enemy officer arrives today in Valor. He is responsible for the production of biological and chemical weapons. Eliminate him!

Key.English: A high enemy government member visits Rashidah today. He wants to take a look at the local ship production in the Rashidah shipyard. Eliminate him!
Key.Spanish: Un alto miembro gubernamental enemigo visita hoy Rashidah. Quiere echar un vistazo a la producción local de barco en el astillero de Rashidah. Elimínelo.
Key.Portuguese: Um membro de governo de inimigo alto visitas Rashidah hoje. Quer tomar uma mirada na produção de barco local no Rashidah shipyard. Elimina-lhe!
Key.Korean: A high enemy government member visits Rashidah today. He wants to take a look at the local ship production in the Rashidah shipyard. Eliminate him!
Key.Japanese: 敵の政府の高官が今日Rashidahを訪れる。彼はRashidah造船所で地元の船の生産を視察するようだ。彼を排除しろ!
Key.Original: A high enemy government member visits Rashidah today. He wants to take a look at the local ship production in the Rashidah shipyard. Eliminate him!

Key.English: The prime minister of Tadistan visits his daughter in Pesto. Eliminate him!
Key.Spanish: El primer ministro de Tadistan visita a su hija en Pesto. Elimínelo.
Key.Portuguese: O premiê de Tadistan visitas sua filha em Pesto. Elimina-lhe!
Key.Korean: The prime minister of Tadistan visits his daughter in Pesto. Eliminate him!
Key.Japanese: Tadistanの首相がPestoに住む娘を訪ねる。彼を排除しろ!
Key.Original: The prime minister of Tadistan visits his daughter in Pesto. Eliminate him!

Key.English: The enemy is testing a new protoype plane on Antigua. Steal it and bring it to the flag at your base.
Key.Spanish: El enemigo está probando un nuevo prototipo de avión en Antigua. Róbelo y llévelo a la bandera de su base.
Key.Portuguese: O inimigo está provando um novo protoype avião em Antiga. Rouba-o e trazer à bandeira em vossa base.
Key.Korean: The enemy is testing a new protoype plane on Antigua. Steal it and bring it to the flag at your base.
Key.Japanese: 敵がAntiguaで新型飛行機のテスト中だ。これを盗み出して基地に持ち帰れ。
Key.Original: The enemy is testing a new protoype plane on Antigua. Steal it and bring it to the flag at your base.

Key.English: An enemy convoy is on route from Ixel to Tandag. Find it and destroy it.
Key.Spanish: Un convoy enemigo está en la ruta de Ixel a Tandag. Encuéntrelo y destrúyalo.
Key.Portuguese: Um convoy de inimigo é em cima rota de Ixel a Tandag. Encontra-o e destruí-lo.
Key.Korean: An enemy convoy is on route from Ixel to Tandag. Find it and destroy it.
Key.Japanese: 敵の護送隊がIxelからTandagへ向かっている。それを見つけて破壊しろ。
Key.Original: An enemy convoy is on route from Ixel to Tandag. Find it and destroy it.

Key.English: An enemy convoy is on route from Corazol to Estrella. Find it and destroy it.
Key.Spanish: Un convoy enemigo está en ruta de Corazol a Estrella. Encuéntrelo y destrúyalo.
Key.Portuguese: Um convoy de inimigo é em cima rota de Corazol a Estrela. Encontra-o e destruí-lo.
Key.Korean: An enemy convoy is on route from Corazol to Estrella. Find it and destroy it.
Key.Japanese: 敵の護送隊がCorazolからEstrellaへ向かっている。それを見つけて破壊しろ。
Key.Original: An enemy convoy is on route from Corazol to Estrella. Find it and destroy it.

Key.English: An enemy convoy is on route from Hunapu to Modesta. Find it and destroy it.
Key.Spanish: Un convoy enemigo está en ruta de Hunapu a Modesta. Encuéntrelo y destrúyalo.
Key.Portuguese: Um convoy de inimigo é em cima rota de Hunapu a Modesta. Encontra-o e destruí-lo.
Key.Korean: An enemy convoy is on route from Hunapu to Modesta. Find it and destroy it.
Key.Japanese: 敵の護送隊がHunapuからModestaへ向かっている。それを見つけて破壊しろ。
Key.Original: An enemy convoy is on route from Hunapu to Modesta. Find it and destroy it.

Key.English: There are some special operations boats in a bay near Pacamac that enemy SF forces use for secret missions. Find them and destroy them.
Key.Spanish: Hay algunos barcos de operaciones especiales en una bahía cerca de Pacamac, las fuerzas SF enemigas los usan para misiones secretas. Encontrarlos y destruirlos.
Key.Portuguese: Há alguns barcas de operações especiais em uma baía próxima Pacamac que inimigo SF força uso para missões secretas. Encontra-lhes e destruir-lhes.
Key.Korean: There are some special operations boats in a bay near Pacamac that enemy SF forces use for secret missions. Find them and destroy them.
Key.Japanese: 特殊部隊の使っているボートがPacamac近くにある。敵特殊部隊が秘密任務に使っているようだ。探して破壊しろ。
Key.Original: There are some special operations boats in a bay near Pacamac that enemy SF forces use for secret missions. Find them and destroy them.

Key.English: Good job. The boats are down.
Key.Spanish: Buen trabajo. Los barcos han sido destruídos.
Key.Portuguese: Trabalho bom. As barcas são abaixo.
Key.Korean: Good job. The boats are down.
Key.Japanese: ボートは破壊された。よくやった。
Key.Original: Good job. The boats are down.

Key.English: The enemy uses a fuelstation located in a camp north of Arcadia to refuel its vehicles. Simple task, destroy it to cut down fuel supplies.
Key.Spanish: El enemigo utiliza una estación de servicio ubicada en un campamento al norte de Arcadia para repostar sus vehículos. Tarea sencilla, destrúyala para cortar el suministro de combustible.
Key.Portuguese: O inimigo utiliza um fuelstation localizou em um norte de acampamento de Arcadia a refuel seus veículos. Tarefa singela, destruí-lo para cortar abaixo fornecimentos de combustível.
Key.Korean: The enemy uses a fuelstation located in a camp north of Arcadia to refuel its vehicles. Simple task, destroy it to cut down fuel supplies.
Key.Japanese: 敵の給油所がArcadiaの北部のキャンプにある。敵は給油所を使って車両に燃料を補給している。 簡単なミッションだ、燃料供給を絶つためにそれを破壊しろ。
Key.Original: The enemy uses a fuelstation located in a camp north of Arcadia to refuel its vehicles. Simple task, destroy it to cut down fuel supplies.

Key.English: A high enemy officer hides on Isla del Vasal or Isla del Vida. He was the one who started the attack agains south Sahrani. Eliminate him!
Key.Spanish: Un alto oficial enemigo se esconde en la Isla Vasal o Isla Vida. Él fue quien inició el ataque contra el sur de Sahrani. Elimínelo.
Key.Portuguese: Uns esconderijos de agente de inimigo altos em Ilha do Vasal ou Ilha do Vida. Seja o que começou o ataque agains do sul Sahrani. Elimina-lhe!
Key.Korean: A high enemy officer hides on Isla del Vasal or Isla del Vida. He was the one who started the attack agains south Sahrani. Eliminate him!
Key.Japanese: 敵高級将校がdel Vasal島かdel Vida島にかくれている。再び南サラーニへの攻撃を始めようとしている者の一人だ。彼を排除しろ!
Key.Original: A high enemy officer hides on Isla del Vasal or Isla del Vida. He was the one who started the attack agains south Sahrani. Eliminate him!

Key.English: The enemy is building a hangar on Trelobada. Intel reports that the enemy will use the hangar to develop submarines. Destroy it before they succeed.
Key.Spanish: El enemigo está construyendo un hangar en Trelobada. Inteligencia reporta que el enemigo va a utilizar el hangar para desarrollar submarinos. Destrúyalo antes de que lo terminen.
Key.Portuguese: O inimigo está construindo um hangar em Trelobada. Intel Informa que o inimigo utilizará o hangar para desenvolver submarinos. Destrói-o dantes de que têm sucesso.
Key.Korean: The enemy is building a hangar on Trelobada. Intel reports that the enemy will use the hangar to develop submarines. Destroy it before they succeed.
Key.Japanese: 敵がTrelobadaに格納庫を建てている。情報によるとこの格納庫で潜水艦を開発中らしい。完成する前に破壊しろ
Key.Original: The enemy is building a hangar on Trelobada. Intel reports that the enemy will use the hangar to develop submarines. Destroy it before they succeed.

Key.English: There is a radio tower in a farm west of Bagango. This is one of the many radio towers that the enemy uses to communicate with its troops. Simple task, destroy it.
Key.Spanish: Hay una torre de radio en una granja al oeste de Bagango. Esta es una de las muchas torres de radio que el enemigo utiliza para comunicarse con sus tropas. Tarea sencilla, destrúyala.
Key.Portuguese: Há uma torre radiofónica em um oeste de granja de Bagango. Isto é um das muitas torres radiofónicas que os usos de inimigo para comunicar com suas tropas. Tarefa singela, destruí-lo.
Key.Korean: There is a radio tower in a farm west of Bagango. This is one of the many radio towers that the enemy uses to communicate with its troops. Simple task, destroy it.
Key.Japanese: Bagango西部の牧場にラジオタワーがある。これは多くある敵軍通信用のタワーの一つだ。それを破壊しろ。
Key.Original: There is a radio tower in a farm west of Bagango. This is one of the many radio towers that the enemy uses to communicate with its troops. Simple task, destroy it.

Key.English: The enemy has a bunker southwest of Mataredo. Enemy government uses this bunker for emergeny situations. Destroy the radar tower there to cut down the ability for them to communicate.
Key.Spanish: El enemigo tiene un búnker al suroeste de Matadero. El gobierno enemigo utiliza este búnker para situaciones de emergencia. Destruya la torre de radar que hay para reducir la capacidad de comunicarse.
Key.Portuguese: O inimigo tem um sudoeste de bunker de Mataredo. Governo de inimigo utiliza este bunker para emergeny situações. Destruir a torre de radar ali para cortar abaixo a capacidade para eles para comunicar.
Key.Korean: The enemy has a bunker southwest of Mataredo. Enemy government uses this bunker for emergeny situations. Destroy the radar tower there to cut down the ability for them to communicate.
Key.Japanese: Mataredoの南西に敵のバンカーがある。 敵の政府は緊急事態にこのバンカーを使用する。 そこにあるレーダータワーを破壊して、敵の通信能力を絶て。
Key.Original: The enemy has a bunker southwest of Mataredo. Enemy government uses this bunker for emergeny situations. Destroy the radar tower there to cut down the ability for them to communicate.

Key.English: There is an enemy depot in a base south of Cabo Juventudo. Destroy all tanks there to weaken the enemy troops.
Key.Spanish: Hay un depósito enemigo en una base al sur del Cabo Juventudo. Destruya todos los tanques, para debilitar las tropas enemigas.
Key.Portuguese: Há um depósito de inimigo em um sul de base de Cabo Juventudo. Destruir todos os tanques ali para debilitar as tropas de inimigo.
Key.Korean: There is an enemy depot in a base south of Cabo Juventudo. Destroy all tanks there to weaken the enemy troops.
Key.Japanese: Caboの南部に敵の集積所がある。 そこにあるすべての戦車を破壊して敵軍を弱体化しろ。
Key.Original: There is an enemy depot in a base south of Cabo Juventudo. Destroy all tanks there to weaken the enemy troops.

Key.English: Enemy forces are testing an enhanced tank version at Alcazar. Your mission is to steal it and bring it to the flag at your base.
Key.Spanish: Las fuerzas enemigas están probando una versión mejorada de tanque en el Alcazar. Su misión es robarlo y llevarlo a la bandera de su base.
Key.Portuguese: Forças de inimigo estão provando uma versão de tanque realçada em Alcazar. Vossa missão é para roubá-lo e trazer à bandeira em vossa base.
Key.Korean: Enemy forces are testing an enhanced tank version at Alcazar. Your mission is to steal it and bring it to the flag at your base.
Key.Japanese: 敵はAlcazarで改良型の戦車をテスト中だ。君の任務はこれを盗み出して基地に持ち帰ることだ。
Key.Original: Enemy forces are testing an enhanced tank version at Alcazar. Your mission is to steal it and bring it to the flag at your base.

Key.English: An enemy scientist is experimenting with volcano technology on Monte Asharah. We don't know yet what it's all about but it is better that he doesn't progress. Eliminate him!
Key.Spanish: Un científico enemigo está experimentando con la tecnología de volcán en Monte Asharah. No sabemos todavía de qué se trata todo esto, pero es mejor que no progresa. Elimínelo.
Key.Portuguese: Um cientista de inimigo é experimenting com tecnologia de vulcão em Monte Asharah. Não sabemos ainda que é tudo aproximadamente mas é melhor que não progride. Elimina-lhe!
Key.Korean: An enemy scientist is experimenting with volcano technology on Monte Asharah. We don't know yet what it's all about but it is better that he doesn't progress. Eliminate him!
Key.Japanese: 敵の科学者がMonte Asharahで火山技術の実験をしている。内容のすべてはまだわからないがやめさせるべきだと判断された。彼を排除しろ!
Key.Original: An enemy scientist is experimenting with volcano technology on Monte Asharah. We don't know yet what it's all about but it is better that he doesn't progress. Eliminate him!

Key.English: The enemy scientist is dead. Good job.
Key.Spanish: El científico enemigo está muerto. Buen trabajo.
Key.Portuguese: O cientista de inimigo é morrido. Bom job.ps.
Key.Korean: The enemy scientist is dead. Good job.
Key.Japanese: 科学者の死亡を確認。よくやった。
Key.Original: The enemy scientist is dead. Good job.

Key.English: There is an enemy depot in a base east of Everon. Destroy all tanks there to weaken the enemy troops.
Key.Spanish: Hay un depósito enemigo en una base al este de Everon. Destruya todos los tanques para debilitar las tropas enemigas.
Key.Portuguese: Há um depósito de inimigo em um este de base de Everon. Destruir todos os tanques ali para debilitar as tropas de inimigo.
Key.Korean: There is an enemy depot in a base east of Everon. Destroy all tanks there to weaken the enemy troops.
Key.Japanese: Everon東部に敵の戦車集積所がある。 そこにあるすべての戦車を破壊して敵軍を弱体化しろ。
Key.Original: There is an enemy depot in a base east of Everon. Destroy all tanks there to weaken the enemy troops.

Key.English: This time we want to provoke the enemy. Find the enemy flag in Parato and bring it back to the flag at your base.
Key.Spanish: Esta vez queremos provocar al enemigo. Encuentre la bandera enemiga en Parato y llévela a la bandera de su base.
Key.Portuguese: Este tempo queremos provocar o inimigo. Encontrar a bandeira de inimigo em Parato e trazê-lo atrás à bandeira em vossa base.
Key.Korean: This time we want to provoke the enemy. Find the enemy flag in Parato and bring it back to the flag at your base.
Key.Japanese: 今回私たちは敵を誘い出したい。 Paratoで敵の旗を見つけ、基地に持ち帰れ。
Key.Original: This time we want to provoke the enemy. Find the enemy flag in Parato and bring it back to the flag at your base.

Key.English: We want to provoke the enemy. Find the enemy flag in Bonanza and bring it back to the flag at your base.
Key.Spanish: Queremos provocar al enemigo. Encuentre la bandera enemiga en Bonanza y llévela de vuelta a la bandera de su base.
Key.Portuguese: Queremos provocar o inimigo. Encontrar a bandeira de inimigo em Bonanza e trazê-lo atrás à bandeira em vossa base.
Key.Korean: We want to provoke the enemy. Find the enemy flag in Bonanza and bring it back to the flag at your base.
Key.Japanese: 今回私たちは敵を誘い出したい。 Bonanzaで敵の旗を見つけ、基地に持ち帰れ。
Key.Original: We want to provoke the enemy. Find the enemy flag in Bonanza and bring it back to the flag at your base.

Key.English: There is a transformer station east of Paraiso. The enemy uses it for its communication relais stations. Simple task, destroy it.
Key.Spanish: Hay un centro de transformación al este de Paraiso. El enemigo lo usa para sus estaciones repetidoras de comunicación. tarea sencilla, destrúyalo.
Key.Portuguese: Há um este de estação do transformador de Paraiso. Os usos de inimigo ele para sua comunicação relais estações. Tarefa singela, destruí-lo.
Key.Korean: There is a transformer station east of Paraiso. The enemy uses it for its communication relais stations. Simple task, destroy it.
Key.Japanese: Paraiso西部に変電所がある。 敵は通信リレーステーションにそれを使用している。 簡単な任務だ、それを破壊しろ。
Key.Original: There is a transformer station east of Paraiso. The enemy uses it for its communication relais stations. Simple task, destroy it.

Key.English: A high enemy government member is visiting Isla de Libertad. This is a good chance to eliminate him!
Key.Spanish: Un alto miembro gubernamental enemigo está de visita en la Isla de Libertad. Esta es una buena oportunidad para eliminarlo.
Key.Portuguese: Um membro de governo de inimigo alto está visitando Ilha de Liberdade. Isto é uma possibilidade boa de lhe eliminar !
Key.Korean: A high enemy government member is visiting Isla de Libertad. This is a good chance to eliminate him!
Key.Japanese: 敵の政府の高官が今日Libertad島を訪れる。彼を排除するいい機会だ
Key.Original: A high enemy government member is visiting Isla de Libertad. This is a good chance to eliminate him!

Key.English: Find the enemy flag in the enemy base in Pesadas and bring it back to the flag at your base.
Key.Spanish: Encuentre la bandera enemiga en la base enemiga en Pesadas y llévela de vuelta a la bandera de su base.
Key.Portuguese: Encontrar a bandeira de inimigo na base de inimigo em Pesadas e trazê-lo atrás à bandeira em vossa base.
Key.Korean: Find the enemy flag in the enemy base in Pesadas and bring it back to the flag at your base.
Key.Japanese: Pesadasの敵基地で敵の旗を見つけ、基地に持ち帰れ。
Key.Original: Find the enemy flag in the enemy base in Pesadas and bring it back to the flag at your base.

Key.English: The enemy is building a prison on Isla de Victoria. Destroy the building so that they can not arrest innocent people.
Key.Spanish: El enemigo está construyendo una prisión en la Isla de Victoria. Destruya el edificio, para que no puedan detener a personas inocentes.
Key.Portuguese: O inimigo está construindo uma prisão em Ilha de Victoria. Destruir o edifício de maneira que não podem prender pessoas inocentes.
Key.Korean: The enemy is building a prison on Isla de Victoria. Destroy the building so that they can not arrest innocent people.
Key.Japanese: 敵はVictoria島に刑務所を建設中だ。無実の人々が逮捕されないように建物を破壊しろ。
Key.Original: The enemy is building a prison on Isla de Victoria. Destroy the building so that they can not arrest innocent people.

Key.English: The enemy is producing biological weapons near Passo Epone. Find the watertower that is needed for the production and destroy it.
Key.Spanish: El enemigo está produciendo armas biológicas cerca de Passo Epone. Encuentre la torre de agua que se necesita para la producción y destrúyala.
Key.Portuguese: O inimigo está produzindo as armas biológicas próximas Passo Epone. Encontrar o watertower aquilo está precisado para a produção e o destruir.
Key.Korean: The enemy is producing biological weapons near Passo Epone. Find the watertower that is needed for the production and destroy it.
Key.Japanese: 敵はPasso Epone近くで生物兵器を製造しているようだ。製造に利用されている給水塔を探して破壊しろ。
Key.Original: The enemy is producing biological weapons near Passo Epone. Find the watertower that is needed for the production and destroy it.

Key.English: There is a radio tower on top of Monte Valor. This is one of the many radio towers that the enemy uses to communicate with its troops. Simple task, destroy it.
Key.Spanish: Hay una torre de radio en la cima del Monte Valor. Esta es una de las muchas torres de radio que el enemigo utiliza para comunicarse con sus tropas. Tarea sencilla, destrúyala.
Key.Portuguese: Há uma torre radiofónica acima de Monte Valor. Isto é um das muitas torres radiofónicas que os usos de inimigo para comunicar com suas tropas. Tarefa singela, destruí-lo.
Key.Korean: There is a radio tower on top of Monte Valor. This is one of the many radio towers that the enemy uses to communicate with its troops. Simple task, destroy it.
Key.Japanese: Valor山の頂上にラジオタワーがある。これは多くある敵軍通信用のタワーの一つだ。簡単な任務だ、それを破壊しろ。
Key.Original: There is a radio tower on top of Monte Valor. This is one of the many radio towers that the enemy uses to communicate with its troops. Simple task, destroy it.

Key.English: The enemy is producing chemical weapons in a base south of Cabo Santa Lucia. Find the watertower that is needed for the production and destroy it.
Key.Spanish: El enemigo está produciendo armas químicas en una base al sur del Cabo Santa Lucía. Encuentra la torre de agua que se necesita para la producción y destrúyala.
Key.Portuguese: O inimigo está produzindo armas químicas em um sul de base de Cabo Santa Lucia. Encontrar o watertower aquilo está precisado para a produção e o destruir.
Key.Korean: The enemy is producing chemical weapons in a base south of Cabo Santa Lucia. Find the watertower that is needed for the production and destroy it.
Key.Japanese: 敵はCabo Santa Lucia南の基地で化学兵器を製造しているようだ。これに利用されている給水塔を探して破壊しろ。
Key.Original: The enemy is producing chemical weapons in a base south of Cabo Santa Lucia. Find the watertower that is needed for the production and destroy it.

Key.English: There is a prison camp in Tiberia. Free the prisoners and bring at least eight prisoners back to your base.
Key.Spanish: Hay un campo de prisioneros en Tiberia. Libere a los prisioneros y lleve al menos ocho presos de vuelta a su base.
Key.Portuguese: Há um acampamento para prisioneiros em Tiberia. Livre os prisioneiros e trazer ao menos oito prisioneiros atrás a vossa base.
Key.Korean: There is a prison camp in Tiberia. Free the prisoners and bring at least eight prisoners back to your base.
Key.Japanese: Tiberiaに捕虜収容所を発見した。 囚人を解放し、少なくとも8人の囚人を基地に連れ帰れ。
Key.Original: There is a prison camp in Tiberia. Free the prisoners and bring at least eight prisoners back to your base.

Key.English: There is a prison camp in Tandag. Free the prisoners and bring at least eight prisoners back to your base.
Key.Spanish: Hay un campo de prisioneros en Tandag. Libere a los prisioneros y lleve al menos ocho presos de vuelta a su base.
Key.Portuguese: Há um acampamento para prisioneiros em Tandag. Livre os prisioneiros e trazer ao menos oito prisioneiros atrás a vossa base.
Key.Korean: There is a prison camp in Tandag. Free the prisoners and bring at least eight prisoners back to your base.
Key.Japanese: Tandagに捕虜収容所を発見した。 囚人を解放し、少なくとも8人の囚人を基地に連れ帰れ。
Key.Original: There is a prison camp in Tandag. Free the prisoners and bring at least eight prisoners back to your base.

Key.English: An enemy officer is on a walk in the forrest Selva de Caza. This is a good chance to arrest him and bring him to your base (only a rescue operator can do that).
Key.Spanish: Un oficial enemigo está caminando en el bosque Selva de Caza. Esta es una buena oportunidad para arrestarlo y llevarlo a su base (sólo un operador de rescate puede hacer eso).
Key.Portuguese: Um agente de inimigo é em um passeio no forrest Selva de Caça. Isto é uma possibilidade boa de lhe prender e trazer a vossa base (só um operador de resgate pode fazer aquele).
Key.Korean: An enemy officer is on a walk in the forrest Selva de Caza. This is a good chance to arrest him and bring him to your base (only a rescue operator can do that).
Key.Japanese: Selva de Cazaの森で敵の将校が散歩中だ。 これは彼を逮捕し、基地に連行するチャンスだ。(レスキューオペレーターだけが逮捕できる)
Key.Original: An enemy officer is on a walk in the forrest Selva de Caza. This is a good chance to arrest him and bring him to your base (only a rescue operator can do that).

Key.English: The enemy support uses the bridges in Dolores to move stuff to the frontline. It is your job to destroy all three bridges there.
Key.Spanish: El soporte enemigo usa los puentes en Dolores para trasladar materiales a la primera línea. Su trabajo es destruir los tres puentes que hay.
Key.Portuguese: O suporte de inimigo utiliza as pontes em Dores para mover material ao frontline. É vosso trabalho para destruir todo três pontes ali.
Key.Korean: The enemy support uses the bridges in Dolores to move stuff to the frontline. It is your job to destroy all three bridges there.
Key.Japanese: 敵の補給部隊は、Doloresの橋を使って物資を前線に運ぶ。 そこにある3つの橋をすべて破壊するのが今回の任務だ。
Key.Original: The enemy support uses the bridges in Dolores to move stuff to the frontline. It is your job to destroy all three bridges there.

Key.English: Good job. The bridges are down.
Key.Spanish: Buen trabajo. Los puentes han sido destruídos.
Key.Portuguese: Trabalho bom. As pontes são abaixo.
Key.Korean: Good job. The bridges are down.
Key.Japanese: よくやった。橋は落とされた。
Key.Original: Good job. The bridges are down.

Key.English: The enemy is testing a new protoype chopper on San Thomas. Steal it and bring it to the flag at your base.
Key.Spanish: El enemigo está probando un nuevo prototipo de helicóptero en San Tomas. Róbelo y llévelo a la bandera de su base.
Key.Portuguese: O inimigo está provando um novo protoype chopper em San Thomas. Rouba-o e trazer à bandeira em vossa base.
Key.Korean: The enemy is testing a new protoype chopper on San Thomas. Steal it and bring it to the flag at your base.
Key.Japanese: San Thomasで敵が新型ヘリコプターをテスト中だ。これを盗み出して基地に持ち帰れ
Key.Original: The enemy is testing a new protoype chopper on San Thomas. Steal it and bring it to the flag at your base.

Key.English: The enemy has all its gold in a bank in Bagango. Destroy the building so that they can't pay their weapon shipments anymore.
Key.Spanish: El enemigo tiene todo su oro en un banco en Bagango. Destruya el edificio de modo que no puedan pagar más sus envíos de armas.
Key.Portuguese: O inimigo tem todo seu ouro em um banco em Bagango. Destruir o edifício de maneira que não podem pagar sua arma shipments anymore.
Key.Korean: The enemy has all its gold in a bank in Bagango. Destroy the building so that they can't pay their weapon shipments anymore.
Key.Japanese: 敵はBagangoにある銀行にすべての金を預けている。 建物を破壊して、これ以上兵器の輸入をできないようにしろ。
Key.Original: The enemy has all its gold in a bank in Bagango. Destroy the building so that they can't pay their weapon shipments anymore.

Key.English: Good job. The bank building is down.
Key.Spanish: Buen trabajo. El edificio del banco ha sido destruído.
Key.Portuguese: Trabalho bom. O edifício de banco é abaixo.
Key.Korean: Good job. The bank building is down.
Key.Japanese: よくやった。銀行は破壊された。
Key.Original: Good job. The bank building is down.

Key.English: The enemy is producing ball bearings in a factory near Paraiso. Destroy the two main buildings to stop the production.
Key.Spanish: El enemigo está produciendo bolas de rodamientos en una fábrica cerca de Paraiso. Destruya los dos edificios principales para detener la producción.
Key.Portuguese: O inimigo está produzindo pelota bearings em uma fábrica próxima Paraiso. Destruir os dois edifícios principais para parar a produção
Key.Korean: The enemy is producing ball bearings in a factory near Paraiso. Destroy the two main buildings to stop the production.
Key.Japanese: 敵はParaiso付近の工場でボールベアリングを生産している。 2つの主要建物を破壊して生産を停止させろ。
Key.Original: The enemy is producing ball bearings in a factory near Paraiso. Destroy the two main buildings to stop the production.

Key.English: The enemy is producing ammunition in a factory near Somato. Destroy the hall and the chimney to stop the production.
Key.Spanish: El enemigo está produciendo municiones en una fábrica cerca de Somato. Destruya la sala y la chimenea para detener la producción.
Key.Portuguese: O inimigo está produzindo munição em uma fábrica próxima Somato. Destruir a sala e a lareira para parar a produção.
Key.Korean: The enemy is producing ammunition in a factory near Somato. Destroy the hall and the chimney to stop the production.
Key.Japanese: 敵はSomato付近の工場で弾薬を生産している。 ホールと煙突を破壊して生産を停止させろ。
Key.Original: The enemy is producing ammunition in a factory near Somato. Destroy the hall and the chimney to stop the production.

Key.English: There is a huge transformer station near Corazol. Destroy the five transfomers to cut down the electrical power.
Key.Spanish: Hay un enorme centro de transformación cerca de Corazol. Destruya los cinco transformadores para reducir la energía eléctrica.
Key.Portuguese: Há uma estação de transformador enorme próximo Corazol. Destruir o cinco transfomers para cortar abaixo o poder elétrico.
Key.Korean: There is a huge transformer station near Corazol. Destroy the five transfomers to cut down the electrical power.
Key.Japanese: Corazolの近くに大きな変電所がある。 5つの変電器を破壊して電力をとめろ。
Key.Original: There is a huge transformer station near Corazol. Destroy the five transfomers to cut down the electrical power.

Key.English: The enemy has a small outpost in a valley near Benoma. Arrest the officer there and bring him back to the flag at your base to get some vital informations.
Key.Spanish: El enemigo tiene un pequeño puesto en un valle cerca Benoma. Detenga al agente de allí y llévelo de vuelta a la bandera de su base para conseguir información vital.
Key.Portuguese: O inimigo tem um pequeno outpost em um vale próximo Benoma. Prendo o agente ali e trazer-lhe atrás à bandeira em vossa base para conseguir algumas informações vitais.
Key.Korean: The enemy has a small outpost in a valley near Benoma. Arrest the officer there and bring him back to the flag at your base to get some vital informations.
Key.Japanese: 敵はBenoma近郊の村に小さな前哨基地を持っています。 重要な情報を入手するため、そこで将校を逮捕し、基地に連行しろ。
Key.Original: The enemy has a small outpost in a valley near Benoma. Arrest the officer there and bring him back to the flag at your base to get some vital informations.

Key.English: The king of Sedia is on vacation in a hotel near Vallejo. He is a good friend of the enemy leaders. Eliminate him!
Key.Spanish: El rey de Sedia está de vacaciones en un hotel cerca de Vallejo. Él es un buen amigo de los líderes enemigos. Elimínelo.
Key.Portuguese: O rei de Sedia é em cima férias em um hotel próximo Vallejo. É um amigo bom dos dirigentes de inimigo. Elimina-lhe!
Key.Korean: The king of Sedia is on vacation in a hotel near Vallejo. He is a good friend of the enemy leaders. Eliminate him!
Key.Japanese: Sediaの王がVallejo付近のホテルで休暇中だ。彼は敵軍リーダーの親しい友人のようだ。彼を排除しろ!
Key.Original: The king of Sedia is on vacation in a hotel near Vallejo. He is a good friend of the enemy leaders. Eliminate him!

Key.English: The king of Sedia is dead. Good job.
Key.Spanish: El rey de Sedia ha muerto. Buen trabajo.
Key.Portuguese: O rei de Sedia é morrido. Trabalho bom.
Key.Korean: The king of Sedia is dead. Good job.
Key.Japanese: Sediaの王は死んだ。よくやった。
Key.Original: The king of Sedia is dead. Good job.

Key.English: One of our own choppers was shot down near Bagango. Find and rescue the crew and bring them back to base. Attention, enemy units are also on the way to the chopper. You have about 15 minutes before they arrive.
Key.Spanish: Uno de nuestros helicópteros fue derribado cerca de Bagango. Encuentre y rescate a la tripulación y llévelos de vuelta a la base. Atención, las unidades enemigas también están en camino hacia el helicóptero. Tiene unos 15 minutos antes de que lleguen.
Key.Portuguese: Um de nosso próprio choppers esteve disparado abaixo próximo Bagango. Encontra e resgatar a tripulação e trazer-lhes atrás para basear. Atenção, unidades de inimigo são também no caminho ao chopper. Tem aproximadamente 15 minutos dantes de que chegam..
Key.Korean: One of our own choppers was shot down near Bagango. Find and rescue the crew and bring them back to base. Attention, enemy units are also on the way to the chopper. You have about 15 minutes before they arrive.
Key.Japanese: 我が軍のヘリコプターがBagango付近で撃墜された。クルーを救出し基地に連れ帰れ。気を付けろ、敵軍もそこに向かっている。15分程度で到着するだろう。
Key.Original: One of our own choppers was shot down near Bagango. Find and rescue the crew and bring them back to base. Attention, enemy units are also on the way to the chopper. You have about 15 minutes before they arrive.

Key.English: One of our own choppers was shot down near Mataredo. Find and rescue the crew and bring them back to base. Attention, enemy units are also on the way to the chopper. You have about 15 minutes before they arrive.
Key.Spanish: Uno de nuestros helicópteros fue derribado cerca de Mataredo. Encuentre y rescate a la tripulación y llévelos de vuelta a la base. Atención, las unidades enemigas también están en camino hacia el helicóptero. Tiene unos 15 minutos antes de que lleguen.
Key.Portuguese: Um de nosso próprio choppers esteve disparado abaixo próximo Mataredo. Encontra e resgatar a tripulação e trazer-lhes atrás para basear. Atenção, unidades de inimigo são também no caminho ao chopper. Tem aproximadamente 15 minutos dantes de que chegam.
Key.Korean: One of our own choppers was shot down near Mataredo. Find and rescue the crew and bring them back to base. Attention, enemy units are also on the way to the chopper. You have about 15 minutes before they arrive.
Key.Japanese: 我が軍のヘリコプターがMataredo付近で撃墜された。クルーを救出し基地に連れ帰れ。気を付けろ、敵軍もそこに向かっている。15分程度で到着するだろう。
Key.Original: One of our own choppers was shot down near Mataredo. Find and rescue the crew and bring them back to base. Attention, enemy units are also on the way to the chopper. You have about 15 minutes before they arrive.

Key.English: The enemy is building a hangar southwest of Roca del Dror. Funny thing is, there is no airfield near that position. So, destroy that hangar before we really know what it is for.
Key.Spanish: El enemigo está construyendo un hangar al suroeste de Roca del Dror. Lo curioso es que no hay pista de aterrizaje cerca de esa posición. Por lo tanto, destruya ese hangar antes de que realmente sapamos para que es.
Key.Portuguese: O inimigo está construindo um sudoeste de hangar de Rocha do Dror. A coisa graciosa é, não há nenhum aeródromo próximo que posição. Tão, destrói que hangar dantes de que realmente sabemos que é para.
Key.Korean: The enemy is building a hangar southwest of Roca del Dror. Funny thing is, there is no airfield near that position. So, destroy that hangar before we really know what it is for.
Key.Japanese: Roca del Drorの南西に敵が格納庫を建設中だが、おかしなことにその近くに飛行場はない。何に使われるか判明する前に破壊しろ。
Key.Original: The enemy is building a hangar southwest of Roca del Dror. Funny thing is, there is no airfield near that position. So, destroy that hangar before we really know what it is for.

Key.English: There is an enemy training facility in San Peregrino. Destroy the main building to cut down their possibilities to train new soldiers.
Key.Spanish: Hay un centro de formación enemigo en San Peregrino. Destruya el edificio principal para reducir la posibilidad de formar nuevos soldados.
Key.Portuguese: Há uma facilidade de formação do inimigo em San Peregrino. Destruir o edifício principal para cortar abaixo suas possibilidades para treinar soldados novos.
Key.Korean: There is an enemy training facility in San Peregrino. Destroy the main building to cut down their possibilities to train new soldiers.
Key.Japanese: San Peregrinoに敵訓練施設がある。新しい兵士を訓練する可能性を減らすために主要な建物を破壊しろ。
Key.Original: There is an enemy training facility in San Peregrino. Destroy the main building to cut down their possibilities to train new soldiers.

Key.English: There is a radio tower on the top of mount Pico de Revolucion. The enemy uses it to communicate. Simple task, destroy it.
Key.Spanish: Hay una torre de radio en la cima del monte Pico de Revolución. El enemigo lo usa para comunicarse. Tarea sencilla, destrúyala.
Key.Portuguese: Há uma torre radiofónica na parte superior de monte Pico de Revolucion. O inimigo utiliza-o para comunicar. Tarefa singela, destruí-lo.
Key.Korean: There is a radio tower on the top of mount Pico de Revolucion. The enemy uses it to communicate. Simple task, destroy it.
Key.Japanese: Pico de Revolucion山の頂上にラジオタワーがある。敵はこれを通信に利用してるようだ。それを破壊しろ。
Key.Original: There is a radio tower on the top of mount Pico de Revolucion. The enemy uses it to communicate. Simple task, destroy it.

Key.English: A new helicopter prototype gets tested on Pita airfield. Destroy it before enemy troops use it.
Key.Spanish: Un nuevo prototipo de helicóptero va a ser probado en el aeródromo de Pita. Destrúyalo antes de que las tropas enemigas lo utilicen.
Key.Portuguese: Um protótipo de helicóptero novo consegue provado em Pita aeródromo. Destrói-o dantes de que tropas de inimigo o utilizam.
Key.Korean: A new helicopter prototype gets tested on Pita airfield. Destroy it before enemy troops use it.
Key.Japanese: Pita飛行場で敵が新型ヘリコプターをテスト中だ。敵軍がこれを使う前に破壊しろ。
Key.Original: A new helicopter prototype gets tested on Pita airfield. Destroy it before enemy troops use it.

Key.English: Base Flag
Key.Spanish: Bandera de base
Key.Portuguese: Bandeira de base
Key.Japanese: Base Flag
Key.Original: Base Flag

Key.English: Attention!!! You are using a NVG scope which is not allowed.\n\nRemoving it now, please choose another scope!
Key.Spanish: ¡¡¡Atención!!! Está utilizando un alcance NVG que no está permitido. \ En \ Extracción ahora, por favor elija otro alcance!
Key.Portuguese: Atenção!!! Está utilizando um NVG atinja que não é dejado.nnRemoving Ele agora, comprazer escolher outro alcance!
Key.Korean: Attention!!! You are using a NVG scope which is not allowed.\n\nRemoving it now, please choose another scope!
Key.Japanese: 注意!!!ナイトビジョンスコープは許可されていません。\n\nスコープを削除しました。ほかのスコープを使ってください!!
Key.Original: Attention!!! You are using a NVG scope which is not allowed.\n\nRemoving it now, please choose another scope!

Key.English: Attention!!! You are using a TI scope which is not allowed.\n\nRemoving it now, please choose another scope!
Key.Spanish: ¡¡¡Atención!!! Está utilizando un ámbito de TI que no está permitido. \ En \ Extracción ahora, por favor elija otro alcance!
Key.Portuguese: Atenção!!! Está utilizando um TI atinja que não é dejado.nnRemoving Ele agora, comprazer escolher outro alcance!
Key.Korean: Attention!!! You are using a TI scope which is not allowed.\n\nRemoving it now, please choose another scope!
Key.Japanese: 注意!!!サーマルイメージスコープは許可されていません。\n\nスコープを削除しました。ほかのスコープを使ってください!!
Key.Original: Attention!!! You are using a TI scope which is not allowed.\n\nRemoving it now, please choose another scope!

Key.English: You are approaching the enemy team area... Turn around immediately!!!!!!!
Key.Spanish: Se está acercando a la zona del equipo enemigo ... Date la vuelta inmediatamente !!!!!!!
Key.Portuguese: Está acercando você o área de equipe do inimigo... Volta ao redor imediatamente!!!!!!!
Key.Korean: You are approaching the enemy team area... Turn around immediately!!!!!!!
Key.Japanese: 敵チームのエリアに近づいています...今すぐ戻ってください!!!!!!
Key.Original: You are approaching the enemy team area... Turn around immediately!!!!!!!

Key.English: Air Drop %1
Key.Spanish: Entrega por paracaídas %1
Key.Portuguese: airdrop %1
Key.Japanese: %1 投下
Key.Original: Air Drop %1

Key.English: No Targets
Key.Spanish: Sin objetivos
Key.Portuguese: Nenhum Objetivo
Key.Japanese: ターゲット無し
Key.Original: No Targets

Key.English: There is a radar tower south of Vagalala. Find it and destroy it.
Key.Spanish: Hay una torre de radar al sur de Vagalala. Encontrarlo y destruirlo.
Key.Portuguese: Aqui é um sul de torre do radar de Vagalala. Encontra-o e destruí-lo.
Key.Korean: There is a radar tower south of Vagalala. Find it and destroy it.
Key.Japanese: Vagalala南部にレーダータワーがある。探して破壊しろ。
Key.Original: There is a radar tower south of Vagalala. Find it and destroy it.

Key.English: A high enemy officer arrives today in a Camp in the Red Spring mine. He is responsible for the death of many civilians. Eliminate him!
Key.Spanish: Un alto oficial enemigo llega hoy en un campamento en la mina Red Spring. Es responsable de la muerte de muchos civiles. ¡Eliminarlo!
Key.Portuguese: Um agente de inimigo alto chega hoje em um Acampamento na mina de Primavera Vermelha. É responsável para a morte de muitos civis. Elimina-lhe!
Key.Korean: A high enemy officer arrives today in a Camp in the Red Spring mine. He is responsible for the death of many civilians. Eliminate him!
Key.Japanese: 敵高級将校が今日Red Spring鉱山にあるキャンプに到着する。彼は多くの民間人の死に関与している。彼を排除しろ!
Key.Original: A high enemy officer arrives today in a Camp in the Red Spring mine. He is responsible for the death of many civilians. Eliminate him!

Key.English: The enemy is testing a new protoype plane at an Airbase. Steal it and bring it to the map at your base.
Key.Spanish: El enemigo está probando un nuevo prototipo de avión en una base aérea. Robarlo y llevarlo a el mapa en su base.
Key.Portuguese: O inimigo está provando um novo protoype avião em um Airbase. Rouba-o e trazer ao mapa em vossa base.
Key.Korean: The enemy is testing a new protoype plane at an Airbase. Steal it and bring it to the map at your base.
Key.Japanese: 敵は航空基地で新型飛行機をテスト中だ。これを盗み出して基地に持ち帰れ
Key.Original: The enemy is testing a new protoype plane at an Airbase. Steal it and bring it to the map at your base.

Key.English: Enemy forces are testing an enhanced tank near Doodstil. Your mission is to steal it and bring it to the map at your base.
Key.Spanish: Las fuerzas enemigas están probando un tanque mejorado cerca Doodstil. Su misión es robar y llevarlo al mapa en su base.
Key.Portuguese: Forças de inimigo estão provando um tanque realçado próximo Doodstil. Vossa missão é para roubá-lo e trazer ao mapa em vossa base..
Key.Korean: Enemy forces are testing an enhanced tank near Doodstil. Your mission is to steal it and bring it to the map at your base.
Key.Japanese: 敵はDoodstil付近で改良型の戦車をテスト中だ。君の任務はこれを盗み出して基地に持ち帰ることだ。
Key.Original: Enemy forces are testing an enhanced tank near Doodstil. Your mission is to steal it and bring it to the map at your base.

Key.English: The enemy is producing chemical weapons in a compound near Lami. Find the cargo truck that has some of the chemicals for the production and destroy it.
Key.Spanish: El enemigo está produciendo armas químicas en un compuesto cerca de Lami. Encontrar el camión de carga que tiene algunos de los productos químicos para la producción y destruirlo.
Key.Portuguese: O inimigo está produzindo armas químicas em uns compostos próximos Lami. Encontrar o cargo caminhão que tem alguns das substâncias químicas para a produção e o destruir.
Key.Korean: The enemy is producing chemical weapons in a compound near Lami. Find the cargo truck that has some of the chemicals for the production and destroy it.
Key.Japanese: Lami付近のコンビナートで敵が化学兵器を製造している。製造な必要な薬品が積まれたカーゴトラックを探して破壊しろ。
Key.Original: The enemy is producing chemical weapons in a compound near Lami. Find the cargo truck that has some of the chemicals for the production and destroy it.

Key.English: The enemy is mining Uran in the Red Spring mine. Your task: destroy the transformer to prevent further mining!
Key.Spanish: El enemigo es la minería urna en la mina de primavera rojo. Su tarea: destruir el transformador para evitar un mayor minera !.
Key.Portuguese: O inimigo é mineiro Uran na mina de Primavera Vermelha. Vossa tarefa: destruir o transformador para impedir mais longínquo mineiro!
Key.Korean: The enemy is mining Uran in the Red Spring mine. Your task: destroy the transformer to prevent further mining!
Key.Japanese: 敵はRed Springでウランを採掘中だ。 ミッション：さらなる鉱業を防ぐために変電器を破壊する！
Key.Original: The enemy is mining Uran in the Red Spring mine. Your task: destroy the transformer to prevent further mining!

Key.English: The enemy is building a hangar at the research base on Imuri Island. There is no airfield near that position. So, destroy that hangar before we really know what it is for.
Key.Spanish: El enemigo es la construcción de un hangar en la base de investigación en Imuri isla. No hay campo de aviación cerca de esa posición. Por lo tanto, destruir ese hangar antes de que realmente sabemos lo que es para.
Key.Portuguese: O inimigo está construindo um hangar na base de busca em Imuri Ilha. não há nenhum aeródromo próximo que posição. Tão, destrói que hangar dantes de que realmente sabemos que é para.
Key.Korean: The enemy is building a hangar at the research base on Imuri Island. There is no airfield near that position. So, destroy that hangar before we really know what it is for.
Key.Japanese: Imuri島の研究拠点に敵が格納庫を建設中だ。その近くに飛行場はない。何に使われるか判明する前に破壊しろ。
Key.Original: The enemy is building a hangar at the research base on Imuri Island. There is no airfield near that position. So, destroy that hangar before we really know what it is for.

Key.English: There is an enemy training facility near Laikoro. Destroy the main building to cut down their possibilities to train new soldiers.
Key.Spanish: Hay un centro de entrenamiento enemigo cerca de Laikoro. Destruya el edificio principal para reducir sus posibilidades de formar a nuevos soldados.
Key.Portuguese: Há uma facilidade de formação do inimigo próximo Laikoro. Destruir o edifício principal para cortar abaixo suas possibilidades para treinar soldados novos.
Key.Korean: There is an enemy training facility near Laikoro. Destroy the main building to cut down their possibilities to train new soldiers.
Key.Japanese: Laikoro付近に敵訓練施設がある。新しい兵士を訓練する可能性を減らすために主要な建物を破壊しろ。
Key.Original: There is an enemy training facility near Laikoro. Destroy the main building to cut down their possibilities to train new soldiers.

Key.English: There is a radio tower on a mountain near Tanouka. The enemy uses it to communicate. Simple task, destroy it.
Key.Spanish: Hay una torre de radio en una montaña cerca Tanooka. El enemigo lo usa para comunicarse. tarea sencilla, lo destruyen.
Key.Portuguese: Há uma torre radiofónica em uma montanha próxima Tanouka. O inimigo utiliza-o para comunicar. Tarefa singela, destruí-lo.
Key.Korean: There is a radio tower on a mountain near Tanouka. The enemy uses it to communicate. Simple task, destroy it.
Key.Japanese: Tanouka付近の山のラジオタワーは敵の通信に利用されてるようだ。それを破壊しろ
Key.Original: There is a radio tower on a mountain near Tanouka. The enemy uses it to communicate. Simple task, destroy it.

Key.English: A new helicopter prototype gets tested on an airstrip. Destroy it before enemy troops use it.
Key.Spanish: Un nuevo prototipo de helicóptero se pone a prueba en una pista de aterrizaje. Destruirlo antes de que las tropas enemigas utilizan.
Key.Portuguese: Um protótipo de helicóptero novo consegue provado em um airstrip. Destrói-o dantes de que tropas de inimigo o utilizam.
Key.Korean: A new helicopter prototype gets tested on an airstrip. Destroy it before enemy troops use it.
Key.Japanese: 飛行場で敵が新型ヘリコプターをテスト中だ。敵軍がこれを使う前に破壊しろ
Key.Original: A new helicopter prototype gets tested on an airstrip. Destroy it before enemy troops use it.

Key.English: There is a artillery cannon somewhere. Destroy it before enemy troops use it to attack Kavala.
Key.Spanish: Hay un cañón de artillería en alguna parte. Destruirlo antes de que las tropas enemigas utilizan para atacar a Kavala.
Key.Portuguese: Aqui é um canhão de artilharia em algum lugar. Destrói-o dantes de que tropas de inimigo o utilizam para atacar Kavala.
Key.Korean: There is a artillery cannon somewhere. Destroy it before enemy troops use it to attack Kavala.
Key.Japanese: どこかに長距離砲がある。敵がこれを使ってKavalaを攻撃する前に破壊しろ
Key.Original: There is a artillery cannon somewhere. Destroy it before enemy troops use it to attack Kavala.

Key.English: A high enemy officer makes holidays near Rereki. Eliminate him !
Key.Spanish: Un alto oficial enemigo está de vacaciones cerca de Rereki. Elimínelo.
Key.Portuguese: Umas marcas de agente de inimigo altas as férias próximas Rereki. Elimina-lhe
Key.Korean: A high enemy officer makes holidays near Rereki. Eliminate him !
Key.Japanese: 敵高級将校がRerekiの近くで休暇を過ごしている。彼を排除しろ!
Key.Original: A high enemy officer makes holidays near Rereki. Eliminate him !

Key.English: The enemy prime minister visits some troops in Saint Julien. Eliminate him !
Key.Spanish: El primer ministro enemigo visita a algunas tropas en Saint Julien. Elimínelo.
Key.Portuguese: As visitas de premiê do inimigo algumas tropas em Julien Santo. Elimina-lhe !
Key.Korean: The enemy prime minister visits some troops in Saint Julien. Eliminate him !
Key.Japanese: 敵の首相がSaint Julien近くの部隊を訪問する。彼を排除しろ!
Key.Original: The enemy prime minister visits some troops in Saint Julien. Eliminate him !

Key.English: There is a radio tower in Galili. The enemy uses it to command its armored troops. Simple task, destroy it.
Key.Spanish: Hay una torre de radio en Galili. El enemigo lo usa para comandar sus tropas blindadas. tarea sencilla, destruirlo.
Key.Portuguese: Há uma torre radiofónica em Galili. O inimigo utiliza-o para mandar suas tropas blindadas. Tarefa singela, destruí-lo.
Key.Korean: There is a radio tower in Galili. The enemy uses it to command its armored troops. Simple task, destroy it.
Key.Japanese: Galiliにラジオタワーがある。敵はこれを装甲車両隊の指揮に利用してるようだ。それを破壊しろ。
Key.Original: There is a radio tower in Galili. The enemy uses it to command its armored troops. Simple task, destroy it.

Key.English: Our forces are in urgent need of supplies. Deliver the supply truck from our Base to the point of destination
Key.Spanish: Nuestras fuerzas están en necesidad urgente de suministros. Entregar el camión de abastecimiento de nuestra base hasta el punto de destino
Key.Portuguese: Nossas forças são em necessidade urgente de fornecimentos. Entregar o caminhão de fornecimento de nossa Base no ponto de destino
Key.Korean: Our forces are in urgent need of supplies. Deliver the supply truck from our Base to the point of destination
Key.Japanese: 友軍が補給を必要としている。基地から補給地点まで補給トラックを届けなくてはならない
Key.Original: Our forces are in urgent need of supplies. Deliver the supply truck from our Base to the point of destination

Key.English: Well done! The friendly forces have got the supplies
Key.Spanish: ¡Bien hecho! Las fuerzas amigas han conseguido los suministros
Key.Portuguese: Bem feito! As forças amistosas têm os fornecimentos
Key.Korean: Well done! The friendly forces have got the supplies
Key.Japanese: よくやった！ 友軍は補給を受け取った
Key.Original: Well done! The friendly forces have got the supplies

Key.English: The enemy has laid naval mines in the entrance to the bay. We need them disarmed to allow us access to the facility nearby.
Key.Spanish: El enemigo ha sembrado minas navales en la entrada de la bahía. Necesitamos desarmados para permitir el acceso a la instalación cercana.
Key.Portuguese: O inimigo tem posto minas navais na entrada à baía. Precisamos-lhes desarmados para deixar-nos acesso à facilidade próxima.
Key.Korean: The enemy has laid naval mines in the entrance to the bay. We need them disarmed to allow us access to the facility nearby.
Key.Japanese: 敵は湾の入り口に機雷を敷設した。 近くの施設にアクセスできるようにするには、機雷を除去しなければならない。
Key.Original: The enemy has laid naval mines in the entrance to the bay. We need them disarmed to allow us access to the facility nearby.

Key.English: The enemy has laid mines on a cross road. We need them disarmed to allow us access to the facility nearby.
Key.Spanish: El enemigo ha sembrado minas en una carretera transversal. Necesitamos desarmados para permitir el acceso a la instalación cercana.
Key.Portuguese: O inimigo tem pôs minas em uma estrada de cruz. Precisamos-lhes desarmados para deixar-nos acesso à facilidade próxima.
Key.Korean: The enemy has laid mines on a cross road. We need them disarmed to allow us access to the facility nearby.
Key.Japanese: 敵は交差道路に地雷を敷設した。 近くの施設にアクセスできるようにするには、地雷を除去しなければならない。
Key.Original: The enemy has laid mines on a cross road. We need them disarmed to allow us access to the facility nearby.

Key.English: Good job! All the mines are cleared
Key.Spanish: ¡Buen trabajo! Todas las minas se borran
Key.Portuguese: Trabalho bom! Todas as minas estão aclaradas
Key.Korean: Good job! All the mines are cleared
Key.Japanese: すべての地雷は除去された
Key.Original: Good job! All the mines are cleared

Key.English: There is a radar tower near Tanouka. Find it and destroy it.
Key.Spanish: Hay una torre de radar cerca de Tanouka. Encontrarlo y destruirlo.
Key.Portuguese: Há uma torre de radar próximo Tanouka. Encontra-o e destruí-lo.
Key.Korean: There is a radar tower near Tanouka. Find it and destroy it.
Key.Japanese: Tanoukaの近くにレーダータワーがある。探して破壊しろ。
Key.Original: There is a radar tower near Tanouka. Find it and destroy it.

Key.English: There is a radio tower near Katkoula. The enemy uses it to command its marine task forces. Simple task, destroy it.
Key.Spanish: Hay una torre de radio cerca de Katkouta. El enemigo lo usa para mandar sus equipos de tareas marinos. tarea sencilla, lo destruyen.
Key.Portuguese: Há uma torre radiofónica próximo Katkoula. O inimigo utiliza-o para mandar suas forças de tarefa marinhas. Tarefa singela, destruí-lo.
Key.Korean: There is a radio tower near Katkoula. The enemy uses it to command its marine task forces. Simple task, destroy it.
Key.Japanese: Katkoulaの近くにラジオの塔がある。 敵は海上タスクフォースを指揮するためにそれを使用される。簡単な任務だ、それを破壊しろ。
Key.Original: There is a radio tower near Katkoula. The enemy uses it to command its marine task forces. Simple task, destroy it.

Key.English: A high enemy officer arrives today at Comms Bravo. He is responsible for the production of biological and chemical weapons. Eliminate him !
Key.Spanish: Un alto oficial enemigo llega hoy a Comms Bravo. Es el responsable de la producción de armas biológicas y químicas. eliminarlo!
Key.Portuguese: Um agente de inimigo alto chega hoje em Comms Bravo. É responsável para a produção de biológico e armas químicas. Elimina-lhe !
Key.Korean: A high enemy officer arrives today at Comms Bravo. He is responsible for the production of biological and chemical weapons. Eliminate him !
Key.Japanese: 敵の高級将校が今日、Comms Bravoに到着する。 彼は生物兵器や化学兵器の生産を担当している。 彼を排除しろ！
Key.Original: A high enemy officer arrives today at Comms Bravo. He is responsible for the production of biological and chemical weapons. Eliminate him !

Key.English: An enemy convoy is on route from Ljinhaven to Petit Nicolet. Find it and destroy it.
Key.Spanish: Un convoy enemigo está ruta de Ljinhaven a Petit Nicolet. Encuéntrelo y destrúyalo.
Key.Portuguese: Um convoy de inimigo é em cima rota de Ljinhaven a Petit Nicolet. Encontra-o e destruí-lo.
Key.Korean: An enemy convoy is on route from Ljinhaven to Petit Nicolet. Find it and destroy it.
Key.Japanese: 敵の護送隊がLjinhavenからPetit Nicoletへ向かっている。それを見つけて破壊しろ。
Key.Original: An enemy convoy is on route from Ljinhaven to Petit Nicolet. Find it and destroy it.

Key.English: An enemy convoy is on route from Qua-Que to Tobakoro. Find it and destroy it.
Key.Spanish: Un convoy enemigo está en ruta de Qua-Que a Tobakoro. Encuéntrelo y destrúyalo.
Key.Portuguese: Um convoy de inimigo é em cima rota de Qua-Que a Tobakoro. Encontra-o e destruí-lo.
Key.Korean: An enemy convoy is on route from Qua-Que to Tobakoro. Find it and destroy it.
Key.Japanese: 敵の護送隊がQua-QueからTobakoroへ向かっている。それを見つけて破壊しろ。
Key.Original: An enemy convoy is on route from Qua-Que to Tobakoro. Find it and destroy it.

Key.English: An enemy convoy is on route from Cerebu to Lega. Find it and destroy it.
Key.Spanish: Un convoy enemigo está en ruta de Cerebu a Lega. Encuéntrelo y destrúyalo.
Key.Portuguese: Um convoy de inimigo é em cima rota de Cerebu a Lega. Encontra-o e destruí-lo.
Key.Korean: An enemy convoy is on route from Cerebu to Lega. Find it and destroy it.
Key.Japanese: 敵の護送隊がセレブからレガに向かっている。それを見つけて破壊しろ。
Key.Original: An enemy convoy is on route from Cerebu to Lega. Find it and destroy it.

Key.English: An enemy convoy is on route from Vatoukolo to Blerik. Find it and destroy it.
Key.Spanish: Un convoy enemigo está en ruta de Vatoukolo a Blerik. Encuéntrelo y destrúyalo.
Key.Portuguese: Um convoy de inimigo é em cima rota de Vatoukolo a Blerik. Encontra-o e destruí-lo.
Key.Korean: An enemy convoy is on route from Vatoukolo to Blerik. Find it and destroy it.
Key.Japanese: VatoukoloからBlerikへのルートに敵の護送隊がいる。 それを見つけて破壊しろ。
Key.Original: An enemy convoy is on route from Vatoukolo to Blerik. Find it and destroy it.

Key.English: A high enemy officer visits the enemy troops today. He is a personal friend of the enemy leader. Eliminate him!
Key.Spanish: Un alto oficial enemigo visita a las tropas enemigas en la actualidad. Él es un amigo personal del líder enemigo. eliminarlo!
Key.Portuguese: Um agente de inimigo alto visita as tropas de inimigo hoje. É um amigo pessoal do dirigente de inimigo. Elimina-lhe!
Key.Korean: A high enemy officer visits the enemy troops today. He is a personal friend of the enemy leader. Eliminate him!
Key.Japanese: 敵の高級将校が今日敵軍を訪問する。 彼は敵のリーダーの個人的な友人だ。 彼を排除しろ！
Key.Original: A high enemy officer visits the enemy troops today. He is a personal friend of the enemy leader. Eliminate him!

Key.English: The enemy uses a fuelstation located near Yanukka to refuel its vehicles. Simple task, destroy it to cut down fuel supplies.
Key.Spanish: El enemigo utiliza una estación de servicio ubicada cerca Yanukka para repostar sus vehículos. Tarea sencilla, destrúyala para cortar el suministro de combustible.
Key.Portuguese: O inimigo utiliza um fuelstation localizou próximo Yanukka a refuel seus veículos. Tarefa singela, destruí-lo para cortar abaixo fornecimentos de combustível.
Key.Korean: The enemy uses a fuelstation located near Yanukka to refuel its vehicles. Simple task, destroy it to cut down fuel supplies.
Key.Japanese: 敵はヤヌッカ近くの燃料ステーションを使って車両に燃料を補給する。 簡単なミッションだ、燃料供給を絶つためにそれを破壊しろ。
Key.Original: The enemy uses a fuelstation located near Yanukka to refuel its vehicles. Simple task, destroy it to cut down fuel supplies.

Key.English: Intel has got some information about a specops camp in the jungle. Find it and eliminate all specops there before they try to sabotage something...
Key.Spanish: Intel tiene alguna información acerca de un campamento specops en la selva. Encontrar y eliminar todas las specops allí antes de que intenten sabotear algo ...
Key.Portuguese: Intel Tem alguma informação sobre um specops acampamento na selva. Encontra-o e eliminar todo specops ali dantes de que provam a sabotagem algo...
Key.Korean: Intel has got some information about a specops camp in the jungle. Find it and eliminate all specops there before they try to sabotage something...
Key.Japanese: 情報部はジャングル内の特殊部隊キャンプに関する情報を手に入れた。キャンプを見つけて特殊部隊が何らかの破壊活動をする前に殺害しろ。
Key.Original: Intel has got some information about a specops camp in the jungle. Find it and eliminate all specops there before they try to sabotage something...

Key.English: There is a radio tower on Yani Islets. This is one of the many radio towers that the enemy uses to communicate with its troops. Simple task, destroy it.
Key.Spanish: Hay una torre de radio en Yani islotes. Esta es una de las muchas torres de radio que el enemigo utiliza para comunicarse con sus tropas. tarea sencilla, destruirlo.
Key.Portuguese: Há uma torre radiofónica em Yani Islotes. Isto é um das muitas torres radiofónicas que os usos de inimigo para comunicar com suas tropas. Tarefa singela, destruí-lo.
Key.Korean: There is a radio tower on Yani Islets. This is one of the many radio towers that the enemy uses to communicate with its troops. Simple task, destroy it.
Key.Japanese: ヤニ島にはラジオタワーがある。 これは、敵がその軍隊と通信するために使用する多くの無線塔の1つだ。 簡単な任務だ、それを破壊しろ。
Key.Original: There is a radio tower on Yani Islets. This is one of the many radio towers that the enemy uses to communicate with its troops. Simple task, destroy it.

Key.English: The enemy has a bunker near Moddergat. Enemy government uses this bunker for emergeny situations. Destroy the radar tower there to cut down the ability for them to communicate.
Key.Spanish: El enemigo tiene un bunker cerca Moddergat. gobierno enemigo utiliza este búnker para situaciones de emergencia. Destruir la torre de radar que hay que reducir la capacidad para que puedan comunicarse.
Key.Portuguese: O inimigo tem um bunker próximo Moddergat. Governo de inimigo utiliza este bunker para emergeny situações. Destruir a torre de radar ali para cortar abaixo a capacidade para eles para comunicar.
Key.Korean: The enemy has a bunker near Moddergat. Enemy government uses this bunker for emergeny situations. Destroy the radar tower there to cut down the ability for them to communicate.
Key.Japanese: 敵はModdergatの近くにバンカーを持っている。 敵の政府は緊急事態にこのバンカーを使用する。 そこにあるレーダータワーを破壊して、敵の通信能力を絶て。
Key.Original: The enemy has a bunker near Moddergat. Enemy government uses this bunker for emergeny situations. Destroy the radar tower there to cut down the ability for them to communicate.

Key.English: There is an enemy tank depot in the west. Destroy all tanks there to weaken the enemy troops.
Key.Spanish: Hay un depósito de tanque enemigo en el oeste. Destruye todos los tanques no para debilitar las tropas enemigas.
Key.Portuguese: Há um depósito de tanque do inimigo no do oeste. Destruir todos os tanques ali para debilitar as tropas de inimigo.
Key.Korean: There is an enemy tank depot in the west. Destroy all tanks there to weaken the enemy troops.
Key.Japanese: 西部に敵の戦車集積所がある。 そこにあるすべての戦車を破壊して敵軍を弱体化しろ。
Key.Original: There is an enemy tank depot in the west. Destroy all tanks there to weaken the enemy troops.

Key.English: There is an enemy tank depot near Lifou. Destroy all tanks there to weaken the enemy troops.
Key.Spanish: Hay un depósito de tanque enemigo cerca de Lifou. Destruye todos los tanques no para debilitar las tropas enemigas.
Key.Portuguese: Há um depósito de tanque do inimigo próximo Lifou. Destruir todos os tanques ali para debilitar as tropas de inimigo.
Key.Korean: There is an enemy tank depot near Lifou. Destroy all tanks there to weaken the enemy troops.
Key.Japanese: Lifouの近くに敵の戦車集積所がある。 そこにあるすべての戦車を破壊して敵軍を弱体化しろ。
Key.Original: There is an enemy tank depot near Lifou. Destroy all tanks there to weaken the enemy troops.

Key.English: This time we want to provoke the enemy. Find the enemy flag in Lailai and bring it back to the map at your base.
Key.Spanish: Esta vez queremos provocar al enemigo. Encuentre la bandera enemiga en Lailai y llévela de vuelta al mapa de su base.
Key.Portuguese: Este tempo queremos provocar o inimigo. Encontrar a bandeira de inimigo em Lailai e trazê-lo atrás ao mapa em vossa base.
Key.Korean: This time we want to provoke the enemy. Find the enemy flag in Lailai and bring it back to the map at your base.
Key.Japanese: 今回私たちは敵を誘い出したい。 Lailaiでの敵の旗を見つけ、基地に持ち帰れ。
Key.Original: This time we want to provoke the enemy. Find the enemy flag in Lailai and bring it back to the map at your base.

Key.English: This time we want to provoke the enemy. Find the enemy flag in Lobaka and bring it back to the map at your base.
Key.Spanish: Esta vez queremos provocar al enemigo. Encuentre la bandera enemiga en Lobaka y llévela de vuelta al mapa de su base.
Key.Portuguese: Este tempo queremos provocar o inimigo. Encontrar a bandeira de inimigo em Lobaka e trazê-lo atrás ao mapa em vossa base.
Key.Korean: This time we want to provoke the enemy. Find the enemy flag in Lobaka and bring it back to the map at your base.
Key.Japanese: 今回私たちは敵を誘い出したい。 ロバカで敵の旗を見つけ、基地に持ち帰れ。
Key.Original: This time we want to provoke the enemy. Find the enemy flag in Lobaka and bring it back to the map at your base.

Key.English: There is a transformer station in Buawa. The enemy uses it for its communication relais stations. Simple task, destroy it.
Key.Spanish: Hay una estación de transformadores en Buawa. El enemigo lo usa para sus estaciones repetidoras de comunicación. tarea sencilla, destrúyala.
Key.Portuguese: Há uma estação de transformador em Buawa. Os usos de inimigo ele para sua comunicação relais estações. Tarefa singela, destruí-lo
Key.Korean: There is a transformer station in Buawa. The enemy uses it for its communication relais stations. Simple task, destroy it.
Key.Japanese: Buawaには変電所がある。 敵は通信リレーステーションにそれを使用する。 簡単な任務だ、それを破壊しろ。
Key.Original: There is a transformer station in Buawa. The enemy uses it for its communication relais stations. Simple task, destroy it.

Key.English: There is an enemy factory near Tavu. Destroy the fuel storage tank to cut down their possibilities to build new vehicles.
Key.Spanish: Hay una fábrica enemiga cerca de Tavu. Destruya el depósito de almacenamiento de combustible para reducir la construcción de nuevos vehículos.
Key.Portuguese: Há uma fábrica de inimigo próximo Tavu. Destruir o tanque de armazenamento do combustível para cortar abaixo suas possibilidades para construir veículos novos.
Key.Korean: There is an enemy factory near Tavu. Destroy the fuel storage tank to cut down their possibilities to build new vehicles.
Key.Japanese: Tavu近くには敵工場がある。 燃料タンクを破壊して新しい車両を作る可能性を減らせ。
Key.Original: There is an enemy factory near Tavu. Destroy the fuel storage tank to cut down their possibilities to build new vehicles.

Key.English: Find the enemy flag in in an old camp and bring it back to the map at your base.
Key.Spanish: Encuentra la bandera enemiga en un antiguo campamento y traerlo de vuelta al mapa en su base.
Key.Portuguese: Encontrar a bandeira de inimigo em um acampamento velho e trazê-lo atrás ao mapa em vossa base.
Key.Korean: Find the enemy flag in an old camp and bring it back to the map at your base.
Key.Japanese: 古いキャンプで敵の旗を見つけて、基地に持ち帰れ。
Key.Original: Find the enemy flag in in an old camp and bring it back to the map at your base.

Key.English: There is an enemy boat factory near Savaka. Destroy the building to cut down their possibilities to build new Boats.
Key.Spanish: Hay una fábrica de barcos enemigos cerca de Savaka. Destruya el edificio para reducir sus posibilidades de construir nuevos barcos.
Key.Portuguese: Há uma fábrica de barca do inimigo próximo Savaka. Destruir o edifício para cortar abaixo suas possibilidades para construir Barcas novas.
Key.Korean: There is an enemy boat factory near Savaka. Destroy the building to cut down their possibilities to build new Boats.
Key.Japanese: サバカの近くには敵の造船所がある。 新しい船を建設する可能性を減らすために建物を破壊しろ。
Key.Original: There is an enemy boat factory near Savaka. Destroy the building to cut down their possibilities to build new Boats.

Key.English: There is an enemy radar on Mont Tanoa. Destroy the radar to cut down their coverage.
Key.Spanish: Hay un radar enemigo en el Mont Tanoa. Destruir el radar para reducir su cobertura.
Key.Portuguese: Há um radar de inimigo em Mont Tanoa. Destruir o radar para cortar abaixo sua cobertura.
Key.Korean: There is an enemy radar on Mont Tanoa. Destroy the radar to cut down their coverage.
Key.Japanese: モン・タノアに敵レーダーがある。 敵のレーダーエリアを減らすためにレーダーを破壊しろ。
Key.Original: There is an enemy radar on Mont Tanoa. Destroy the radar to cut down their coverage.

Key.English: There is an Officer hiding in Imone. Capture him and get him to our base for questioning.
Key.Spanish: Hay un oficial que oculta en la imagen. capturarlo y llevarlo a nuestra base para ser interrogado.
Key.Portuguese: Há um Agente escondendo em Imone. Captura-lhe e conseguir a nossa base para questionar.
Key.Korean: There is an Officer hiding in Imone. Capture him and get him to our base for questioning.
Key.Japanese: Imoneに将校がいる。 彼を捕まえ、尋問のために基地に連行しろ。
Key.Original: There is an Officer hiding in Imone. Capture him and get him to our base for questioning.

Key.English: in Namuvaka
Key.Spanish: en Namuvaka
Key.Portuguese: Em Namuvaka
Key.Japanese: Namuvakaに
Key.Original: in Namuvaka

Key.English: in Sosovu
Key.Spanish: en Sosovu
Key.Portuguese: Em Sosovu
Key.Japanese: Sosovuに
Key.Original: in Sosovu

Key.English: An enemy officer is on a walk in a forrest near Kotomo. This is a good chance to arrest him and bring him to your base.
Key.Spanish: Un oficial enemigo está caminando por un bosque cerca de Kotomo. Esta es una buena oportunidad para arrestarlo y llevarlo a su base.
Key.Portuguese: Um agente de inimigo é em um passeio em um forrest próximo Kotomo. Isto é uma possibilidade boa de lhe prender e trazer a vossa base.
Key.Korean: An enemy officer is on a walk in a forrest near Kotomo. This is a good chance to arrest him and bring him to your base.
Key.Japanese: Kokomoの近くの森で敵の将校が散歩中だ。 これは彼を逮捕し、基地に連行するチャンスだ。
Key.Original: An enemy officer is on a walk in a forrest near Kotomo. This is a good chance to arrest him and bring him to your base.

Key.English: There is an Officer on an north island. Capture him and get him to our base for questioning.
Key.Spanish: Hay un oficial en una isla al norte. capturarlo y llevarlo a nuestra base para ser interrogado.
Key.Portuguese: Há um Agente em uma ilha do norte. Captura-lhe e conseguir a nossa base para questionar.
Key.Korean: North island에 장교가 있습니다. 심문을 위해 잡아 본부로 데려오십시오.
Key.Japanese: 北の島に将校がいる。 彼を捕まえ、尋問のために基地に連行しろ。
Key.Original: There is an Officer on an north island. Capture him and get him to our base for questioning.

Key.English: The enemy is testing a new protoype chopper at Tanoa Airport. Steal it and bring it to the map at your base.
Key.Spanish: El enemigo está probando un nuevo prototipo de helicóptero en Tanoa Airport. Róbelo y llévelo al mapa de su base.
Key.Portuguese: O inimigo está provando um novo protoype chopper em Tanoa Aeroporto. Rouba-o e trazer ao mapa em vossa base.
Key.Korean: Tanoa Airport에서 적인 새로운 실험헬기를 운용하고있습니다. 들어가 기체를 훔쳐 본부로 가져오십시오.
Key.Japanese: 敵はタンパ空港で新しい試作ヘリコプターをテストしている。 それを盗んで、あなたの基地に持ち帰れ。
Key.Original: The enemy is testing a new protoype chopper at Tanoa Airport. Steal it and bring it to the map at your base.

Key.English: There is a temporary prison camp that has been discovered at Rautake. Free the prisoners and bring at least eight prisoners back to your base.
Key.Spanish: Hay un campo de prisioneros temporal que se ha descubierto en Rautake. Libere a los presos y llevar al menos ocho presos de vuelta a su base.
Key.Portuguese: Há um acampamento para prisioneiros provisório aquilo tem sido descoberto em Rautake. Livre os prisioneiros e trazer ao menos oito prisioneiros atrás a vossa base.
Key.Korean: 적군이 지역주민들을 모아 Rautake 주변에 임시 수용소를 설치하였습니다. 수용소에 있는 인원을 구출하고, 최소 8명이상과 함께 안전하게 본부로 귀환하십시오.
Key.Japanese: Rautakeで臨時収容所を発見した。 囚人を解放し、少なくとも8人の囚人を基地に連れ帰れ。
Key.Original: There is a temporary prison camp that has been discovered at Rautake. Free the prisoners and bring at least eight prisoners back to your base.

Key.English: The Enemy are rounding up the locals and have made a temporary prison camp at Ipota. Free the prisoners and bring at least eight prisoners back to your base.
Key.Spanish: El enemigo está acorralando a la gente del lugar y han hecho un campo de prisioneros temporal en Ipota. Libere a los prisioneros y lleve al menos ocho de ellos de vuelta a su base.
Key.Portuguese: O Inimigo está arrendondando acima dos lugareños e tem feito um acampamento para prisioneiros provisório em Ipota. Livre os prisioneiros e trazer ao menos oito prisioneiros atrás a vossa base.
Key.Korean: 적군이 지역주민들을 모아 Ipota 주변에 임시 감옥을 만들었습니다. 감옥에 있는 주민들을 풀어주시고 최소 8명이상을 본부로 안전히 데려오십시오.
Key.Japanese: 敵は地元民を捕まえて、イポータに臨時収容所を作った。 囚人を解放し、少なくとも8人の囚人を基地に連れ帰れ。
Key.Original: The Enemy are rounding up the locals and have made a temporary prison camp at Ipota. Free the prisoners and bring at least eight prisoners back to your base.
